('Hide and Luig', 2643, 'A whimsical point-and-click hide-and-seek adventure where your only goal is to find the ever-elusive Luig&amp;mdash;who insists on hiding inside the weirdest objects imaginable. Explore playful scenes, click around, and uncover Luig&amp;rsquo;s latest hideout in this charmingly absurd journey of curiosity and surprise.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Magic Piano Music', 2644, 'Ready to become a piano master? In Magic Piano Music, tap the magic tiles to follow the beats and play your favorite music. Follow the rhythm of the music and click with precision, dont miss any notes. The game will end after three misses. Theres tons of music here like classic piano music, pop music and more! Every song will take you on an immersive arcade rhythm adventure.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Girls Fashion Nail Salon', 2645, 'Welcome to Girls Fashion Nail Salon, a casual dress-up game for girls. If you are a girl who loves makeup or has a specific interest in fashion, then this nail salon simulator is just designed for you. Get ready to dive into the world of fashion and create your own masterpiece.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('I Am Security', 2646, 'Have you ever wanted to be a hardened security officer and be on the front lines of maintaining order? In I Am Security, an ultra-realistic role-playing simulator, you play the role of a professional security guard. You decide whether or not to allow them to enter. Some guests may try to sneak in with prohibited items and find these hidden items. Performs tasks in a variety of scenarios to identify suspicious persons.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Dark Sprint', 2647, 'Dark Sprint is a fast-paced, adrenaline-pumping runner set in a shadowy, mysterious world. Dash through eerie landscapes filled with traps, crumbling paths, and lurking dangers as you guide your character through the darkness. With precise timing and quick reflexes, avoid deadly obstacles and unlock new areas cloaked in secrets. Collect glowing orbs, power-ups, and hidden relics to boost your speed and score. The deeper you run, the darker and more thrilling it becomes. With stylish visuals, intense gameplay, and haunting soundscapes, Dark Sprint offers an unforgettable running experience. Can you outrun the darkness and survive the night?', 'use mouse or touch screen on mobile to play game', 'English'),
('Mahjong tralalero tralala', 2648, 'Mahjong Tralalero Tralala &amp;ndash; Match, Relax &amp;amp; Enjoy the Fun! Dive into a joyful Mahjong experience like no other! Match colorful tiles featuring , animals, and silly surprises &amp;ndash; all while grooving to the catchy Tralalero Tralala soundtrack. With playful visuals, simple gameplay, and cheerful vibes, this game is perfect for kids and casual players alike. Can you clear all the tiles before the music ends?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sweet Monster   Pull Out Pin', 2649, 'Sweet Monster - Pull Out Pin is a fun, challenging, and brain-training puzzle game where your mission is to help a lovable monster escape tricky traps and collect delicious treats! Use your logic to pull the right pins in the right order and guide the sweet monster to safety. Each level is packed with clever traps, dangerous enemies, lava pools, and hidden surprises. You must think before you pull, or the monster might fall into danger! Pull the pins, avoid obstacles, defeat enemies, and make your way to candy heaven. With vibrant graphics, smooth controls, and engaging gameplay, Sweet Monster - Pull Out Pin offers a fun experience for play', 'Use mouse to play game', 'English'),
('Shish Fruit', 2650, 'Aim and shoot the falling juicy fruits of many types. Shoot multiple fruits with one shish for combos. Get the best scores in Classic and Time Trial modes.', 'Click or touch and drag to aim Then release to shoot', 'English'),
('Candy Match Puzzle', 2651, 'Dive into a delightful puzzle experience with Candy Puzzle Match, where matching candies is all about tapping! Simply tap on groups of two or more adjacent candies of the same color to clear them from the board. The more candies you clear at once, the higher your score! Watch the board shift and cascade with every move as you complete deliciously fun objectives. With colorful visuals and satisfying chain reactions, this game is perfect for fans of casual and relaxing puzzle games.', 'Tap candies to clear', 'English'),
('College Basketball Games Today', 2652, 'College Basketball Games Today is the ultimate arcade-style college basketball game for fans who love fast-paced sports action! Play solo or challenge a friend in the exciting 2-player basketball mode. With fun cartoon graphics and characters inspired by legendary basketball players, this game offers a thrilling mix of dunks, 3-pointers, and buzzer-beaters. Perfect for quick matches or full tournaments, its the ideal basketball game for kids and adults alike. Whether playing a quick match or climbing the ranks, College Basketball Games Today brings classic basketball arcade gameplay with a modern twist. Get ready to hit the court,', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('SpaceFrontier', 2653, 'Control the safe launch of the rocket. Rockets have multiple levels. Seize the opportunity to safely separate the rocket levels. Rockets can be upgraded, and the higher the level, the more grades there are. Rockets can reach other planets when they fly to a certain height. Come and try to see how high the rocket you control can fly.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Italian Neuro Beast Battle Defense', 2654, 'Italian Neuro Beast Battle: Create Defense &amp;mdash; is a game about Italian meme neuro animals, which are brainrots. Build the best defense using 6 unique neuro animals, each with its own abilities. Show your strategic skills! In addition, each hero has its own level and gradually pumps up, becoming stronger. The game has three modes: - Normal &amp;mdash; recommended for most players. - Turbo &amp;mdash; for those who love action. - Hardcore &amp;mdash; for experienced players.', 'Controls by tapping and clicking - Tap the screen to select a spawn location for heroes - Then click on the hero icons to spawn them - Pay attention to the price of heroes and your current balance', 'English'),
('HangertheGuy', 2655, 'Click the screen, and the characters hand can emit a thin thread, which hooks the top and swings. Use inertia to control the character to safely reach the finish line. There will be various obstacles along the way, so avoid touching them. Come and play.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Flippin Fingers', 2656, 'Prepare yourselfs with, Flippin Fingers is here! Win, survive and be the best! Your fingers will stand to a fight you cant even imagine! Flippin Fingers will take you to the sky, where you will battle to death using your own finger. Is your finger faster than the others?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Gangsta Duel', 2657, 'Gangsta Duel is an exciting street duel game that brings you into a world of battles. Face off against the street Gangsta. In this game, you will fight a large wave of enemies. Use your skills to attack and destroy all your enemies. Unleash powerful combat skills and make your enemies feel the absolute blow.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Merge the Planets: 2048!', 2658, 'This game is in the style of the classic 2048! Connect planets ! Connect as many as possible to get the biggest planet! Collect points and compete with friends or colleagues! Enjoy your game!', 'At first it will be easy to connect planets but over time there will be more and more of them Once you connect the biggest planet it will disappear and you will get the most points', 'English'),
('Line Shape Puzzle', 2659, 'Line Shape Puzzle challenges players to connect matching shapes with lines while avoiding obstacles. With sleek graphics and intuitive controls, this addictive puzzle game offers endless brain-teasing fun. Strategize your moves to navigate increasingly complex patterns, earning rewards and unlocking new challenges. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.coolcrazygames.com/''&gt;https://www.coolcrazygames.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Perfect Asmr Cleaning', 2660, 'Immerse yourself in home cleaning and personal care with Perfect ASMR Cleaning! This is a casual cleaning simulator game where you can experience the whole process of cleaning work, such as washing carpets and trimming cat nails. Finish each task with full patience and enjoy the perfect sound of teeth polishing, cutting, and trimming. Relieve your pressure in all the virtual effects and have fun!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Dress up Thumbelina', 2661, 'Dress up Thumbelina, the graceful little maiden whose name means little thumb because of her tiny size. This character is meant to illustrate the lovely fairytale.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('2 Player BlockMiner Escape', 2662, 'Miners, run quickly to the minecart! The miners have jumped in and are escaping from the giant zombie. Never look back and help Steve and Alex. They need to escape the mine, but first they must reach the gold chest at the end. Help them get to the gold chest. The mine is very dangerous &amp;mdash; there are obstacles and spiders everywhere. Reach the gold chest safely!', 'Press W or the Up Arrow key to jump Playable on both mobile and PC Double jump available', 'English'),
('Fruit Clash', 2663, 'Welcome to Fruit Clash, the ultimate fruit merge adventure! Combine identical fruits to create bigger, juicier ones and unlock amazing surprises! Simple, Addictive Merge Gameplay Drag and merge fruits on the board. The more you merge, the more powerful and rare your fruits become! Grow Your Fruit Garden Start with basic fruits and evolve them into legendary superfruits. Watch your garden grow into a colorful paradise! Unlock Rare Fruits &amp;amp; Bonuses Discover dozens of fruit types, from apples and oranges to exotic hybrids! Unlock boosters and special rewards along the way. Explore Fun Stages &amp;amp; Challenges Each level brings new pu', 'Addictive merge gameplay Colorful and fun fruit graphics Smooth drag-and-drop controls Works perfectly on desktop and mobile browsers No installation required', 'English'),
('WavyTrip', 2664, 'Control the plane through obstacles. There will be many obstacles during the flight of the aircraft, and grasp the strength and timing to make the aircraft safely through the obstacles. You can also get gold rewards during the flight, and gold can unlock other planes, come and play.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Atom Fall', 2665, 'Atom Fall is a thrilling arcade survival game that will put your reflexes and focus to the ultimate test In this minimalist yet intense experience you control a small glowing ball the atom trapped inside a constantly spinning centrifuge The centrifuge is equipped with deadly rotating blades that shift in speed and position as the game progresses making every second a fight for survival.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Craft Man Vs Giant TNT', 2666, 'Are you ready to enter a crazy world full of giants and TNT? Craftsman vs Giant TNT is an exciting Minecraft-style game that challenges your creativity, strategy and courage. Play as a brave craftsman in a dangerous world. Choose between two different modes: Destroy TNT or City TNT. Build fortifications and use weapons to repel giant enemies.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Bombardino Crocodilo Terror Jumpscare', 2667, 'Welcome to Bombardino Crocodilo: Terror Jumpscare, a spine-chilling horror game that will test your nerves, reflexes, and courage. In this twisted nightmare, you take on the role of an unfortunate visitor trapped inside a cursed, abandoned mansion. Your mission? Collect all the creepy dolls scattered across the dark, decrepit corridors and escape before its too late. Sounds simple? Think again.', 'wasd move', 'English'),
('Red and Blue Hugli Wugli', 2668, 'The Hugli Wugli brothers are lost in the castle, and in the first game of the series, you must help them. These mischievous brothers have strapped hoverboards to their feet and are trying to escape from the castle. But beware &amp;mdash; the castle is full of traps, and you need to be careful! Find the red and blue keys as quickly as possible. Watch out for the zombie in the castle &amp;mdash; if you get caught, you lose.', 'Use the WASD and Arrow keys to move Collect all the coins find the red and blue keys and head to the door Playable on both mobile and PC', 'English'),
('Sprunki Block Challenge', 2669, 'Sprunki Block Challenge is a super fun and free to play online game that kids will absolutely love! Join the adorable Sprunki on a block breaking adventure full of surprises. Your mission is simple but exciting: click on the right blocks to help Sprunki fall safely to the ground. But watch out: tricky obstacles and floating platforms make each level a clever puzzle to solve.', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Fish Evolution 3d', 2670, 'Ready to have the most exciting evolution adventure in Fish Evolution 3D? This is not just another casual game. Its a fun running and collecting experience. Your fish evolves in real-time as you swim through a colorful 3D platform world! Start as a tiny fish and collect more fish to grow bigger, faster, and cooler. Avoid dangerous traps like a hook or through the lazy door.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Baby Panda Dentist Care', 2671, 'Teeth are so important! Want to show a beautiful smile? Want to have white and healthy teeth? Come to Baby Panda Dentist Care to see what problems the baby animals have with their teeth and give them the appropriate treatment. This is a casual doctor simulation game. You will play as a dentist and accept every cute animal with dental problems.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Twisted Auto Metal', 2672, 'Twisted Auto Metal is an explosive vehicular combat game set in a post-apocalyptic wasteland where chaos reigns and only the deadliest drivers survive. Inspired by classic titles like Twisted Metal, this high-octane shooter puts players behind the wheel of brutalized, weaponized cars, including the iconic Nissan Skyline, now reborn as a steel-clad death machine. In this world, there are no rules&amp;mdash;only carnage, speed, and the desperate hunger to outlast and obliterate the competition.', 'WASD move', 'English'),
('Ninja brainrot Slice', 2673, 'Ninja Brainrot Slice is an endless arcade game that puts your ninja reflexes to the ultimate test! Instead of slicing fruit, you&amp;rsquo;ll slash through the crazy heads of your favorite Brainrot characters &amp;mdash; Tung Tung, Sahur, Crocodilo, and Tralala. Swipe fast, build combos, and climb the leaderboards as the heads fly across the screen. But be careful &amp;mdash; one wrong slice into a bomb and your run is over! Fast-paced, funny, and addictive &amp;mdash; Ninja Brainrot Slice turns chaos into a slicing challenge like no other.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('StickManHook', 2674, 'Complete the adventure with the hero, The game has multiple levels, each level has a number of anchor points, the use of inertia, so that the hero through the anchor point to reach the end.Through the level will be rewarded with gold, gold can be used to unlock new heroes, come to experience.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Echoes of Bushido', 2675, 'Echoes of Bushido Honor in motion. Precision is survival. In Echoes of Bushido, you are the last hope of a fallen samurai clan. With only your instincts and discipline, toggle between paths as deadly weapons fly your way. Dodge with precision, collect sacred stars, and carve your legend into the scrolls of time. Master the rhythm of survival in a world where one wrong move means the end &amp;mdash; and only the focused endure.', 'Click to go other side and avoid weapons', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Boots n Bounds', 2676, 'Boots &amp;amp; Bounds Saddle up and hang tight &amp;mdash; it&amp;rsquo;s a wild ride! In Boots &amp;amp; Bounds, you take control of a fearless rider atop a rampaging rhino, thundering through wild terrain where danger comes at you fast. Dodge, leap, and react with perfect timing as a nonstop stream of obstacles barrels toward you. One wrong move, one missed jump &amp;mdash; and it&amp;rsquo;s game over. With simple one-tap controls and pulse-pounding action, every second counts in this high-speed endless runner. Collect bonuses, break records, and prove you&amp;rsquo;ve got the guts (and reflexes) to ride the beast and survive the stampede.', 'Click to Jump and Avoid obstacles this way', 'English'),
('Sorting Fruits Game', 2677, 'Sorting Fruits is a relaxing and educational game where players organize colorful fruits into their correct baskets. Theres no timer &amp;mdash; just smooth, stress-free gameplay designed to boost focus and sorting skills. With beautiful visuals and easy drag-and-drop controls, it&amp;rsquo;s a perfect game for kids, families, and casual players. Add Sorting Fruits to your platform and offer your audience a calm, enjoyable gaming experience that improves observation and categorization abilities.', 'Mobile Tap on a tube to select it Tap on another tube to pour the top fruit slices Desktop Left Click on a test tube to pick it up Left Click again on another tube to transfer fruits', 'English'),
('AnimalRush', 2678, 'Help your pet get to the finish line safely. There are multiple corners in the game, and the pet is controlled to reach the end through the corner at the exact time.Coins can be obtained in the game, the game has multiple pets, and coins can unlock pets. Come and play.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Onet Mahjong Connect', 2679, 'Onet Mahjong Connect is an easy and fun puzzle game where players match identical tiles. The goal is to connect two matching tiles. Tiles can be linked if they can be joined using three or fewer straight lines. With many levels to enjoy, the game offers a relaxing and engaging experience &amp;mdash; perfect for taking a break and sharpening your mind!', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game', 'English'),
('Tap Tap Racing', 2680, 'Tap Tap Racing &amp;ndash; Retro Three-Lane Arcade Racer! Buckle up and get ready for high-speed, retro-style racing thrills in Tap Tap Racing, the addictive arcade car game that&amp;rsquo;s easy to play and hard to master! Tap left or right to switch lanes, dodge wild obstacles, and collect golden coins in this endless three-lane road challenge. Experience the charm of pixel art, the pulse of synthwave music, and the rush of fast-paced gameplay &amp;ndash; all in one unforgettable mobile racing game. Welcome to the World of Tap Tap Racing Take control of your pixel car and race down endless neon highways. The rules? Simple. There are three roads, and your job', 'Keyboard Z X C or tap to play', 'English'),
('Cosmic Connector', 2681, 'Embark on a stellar puzzle adventure! In Cosmic Connector, draw a continuous energy path to unite the stars. Plan your connections wisely to avoid crossing the beam and outmaneuver the dangerous rogue particle.', 'Left Click or Finger Tap', 'English'),
('FrogTap', 2682, 'Adventure with animals. Take the time to help the animal jump from one platform to the platform above, Avoid touching the spikes above. During the game, you can earn diamonds, which are used to unlock new animals.Come and experience it.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Soldier Run Evolution', 2683, 'Soldier Run Evolution is a fun platform running game that includes soldier evolution and puzzle elements in one epic adventure. Lead your soldier through exciting levels, attack, and shoot enemies. Move your soldiers through an increasing number of doors, thus growing your ranks. Increase weapon power to unlock different stages of evolution.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Graduation Makeup Trends', 2684, 'Discover the latest makeup trends with our Graduation Makeup Trends game! Its time to glam up as you prepare for the most memorable day of your life. Get ready to experiment with stunning looks that will make heads turn as you walk across the stage. From bold and fierce to soft and elegant, this game offers a variety of makeup options to suit your style. We bring 3 BFFs, each with a unique style, many makeup options, stunning dresses, and accessories for your inspiration. Mixed with floral printed dresses, golden jewelry, and holographic accessories, you will find everything you need to help these girls make a statement.', 'Use your mouse to play the game on a desktop or tap to play on mobile devices', 'English'),
('DIY Paper Doll Diary', 2685, 'Welcome to DIY Paper Doll Diary, a casual DIY game where you design your own house with different themes. You are free to unleash your creativity to decorate the room, build coffee shops, and design play yards. Challenge your imagination, logic, and spatial ability because you have to furnish the room from scratch. Yet, do not worry. Here are plenty of items for you to choose from. Just enjoy the transformation of an empty room into a lively and cozy place!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Fantasy Anime Dress Up', 2686, 'In the world of fantasy anime dress-up, enthusiasts dive into a vibrant universe where imagination knows no bounds. Here, you can create and customize characters from ethereal elves to daring warriors, dressing them in a vast array of magical outfits and accessories. Every piece tells a story, from enchanted cloaks to gleaming armor, allowing players to express their creativity and craft unique avatars that embody their wildest fantasies. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.gamesunblockedgames.com''&gt;https://www.gamesunblockedgames.com&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Horror School Detective Story', 2687, 'Ready to enter a horror school full of scares and mysteries? In Horror School: Detective Story, you&amp;rsquo;ll play the role of a brave detective. Solve the mysteries layered on top of each other at the school. Each scene is tense and exciting, full of suspense and the unknown! Choose the complexity of the scenario to start your challenge.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Italian Brainrot Hunter', 2688, 'Grab your weapon and shoot all the incoming monsters! You need to reach the helicopter safely. Brainrot monsters are everywhere &amp;mdash; theyve invaded the city. Trallela is the strongest monster, and you must defeat it. Take it down and claim victory. Grab your gun and fire!', 'Use the WASD keys to move Shoot and defeat all incoming enemies Reach your helicopter safely Playable on both mobile and PC', 'English'),
('Doodle Dash', 2689, 'In this playful physics-based puzzle game, players draw lines to create paths for a bouncy ball to travel. The goal is to help the ball go as far as possible by using clever lines and strategic timing. The farther the ball rolls, the more ink you earn &amp;mdash; and more ink means more possibilities! Use your ink to upgrade your ball, unlock new types of balls, and reach even greater distances. With a fun doodle-style art direction and quirky mechanics, this game blends creativity, planning, and light-hearted challenge into one endlessly replayable experience.', 'Use the left mouse button or finger to draw the line', 'English'),
('Italian Brainrot Candy', 2690, '&amp;ldquo;Italian Brainrot Candy&amp;rdquo; is an electrifying game where your mission is to match identical blocks to earn extra time. Each time you match identical blocks, you earn a precious second, but beware: if time runs out, it&amp;rsquo;s game over! Challenge your reflexes and matching skills in this thrilling and addictive game, where every move counts to avoid imminent defeat.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('TinyGameBox', 2691, 'A variety of puzzle games are gathered together, all of which are very fun and can exercise your reaction ability. Come and give it a try.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Brick Breaker Gala', 2692, 'Shatter bricks and shine in Brick Breaker Gala, a thrilling arcade game! Strategically launch balls, unleash powerful power-ups, and demolish colorful brick walls across countless levels. Earn stars with high scores to advance in the dazzling Summer Gala, claiming fantastic rewards! Collect coins to enhance your gameplay through a robust upgrade system, boosting your balls, power-ups, and lives. Conquer challenges with skill and precision in this visually stunning and endlessly addictive brick-breaking adventure!', 'Use mouse or tap to set ball shoot direction and destroy bricks', 'English'),
('Snaily Braver (Europe Adventure)', 2693, 'Join Snaily Braver on a Grand European Adventure! Get ready to embark on a charming journey with the worlds most intrepid snail! Meet Snaily, a small adventurer with a big heart and an even bigger dream: to capture the perfect selfie in Europes most famous cities. He&amp;rsquo;s packed his shell and is ready for an unforgettable trip, but he cant do it without you! Guide our courageous hero through the stunning landscapes of Paris, Amsterdam, and London in this delightful platforming adventure. Leap across rooftops, dodge the grumpy Fog Police, and outsmart mischievous crows as you explore beautifully crafted levels inspired by real-world locations', 'Simple amp Intuitive Controls Mastering Snailys moves is easy and fun whether youre at a desk or on the go On PC Use the Arrow Keys to run left and right and press the Up Arrow to jump Ready to defend yourself Hit the Spacebar to launch a spitball', 'English'),
('Unicorn Coloring Challenge', 2694, 'Unicorn Coloring Challenge is a magical and delightful coloring game that will spark creativity in kids and adults alike! Dive into a world of rainbow-colored unicorns, sparkling stars, and enchanted landscapes. Grab your digital crayons, paints, and brushes to bring each adorable unicorn to life. With endless colors to choose from, you can create dazzling designs, mix and match patterns, and let your imagination run wild. Perfect for little artists who love magical creatures, glittery adventures, and fun challenges. Let the unicorn magic begin and see who can make the most fabulous masterpiece!', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Chromatch', 2695, 'Chromatch &amp;ndash; Test Your Reflexes, Match Your Colors! Get ready for Chromatch, the fast-paced color-matching challenge that keeps you on your toes! A spinning wheel divided into four vibrant color sections awaits your precision. Your task is simple: throw the arrow of a given color and hit the matching section. But be careful&amp;mdash;land on the wrong color, and you&amp;rsquo;ll lose one of your three lives. As the wheel speeds up, your reflexes, timing, and focus will be put to the ultimate test. Easy to pick up but hard to master, Chromatch delivers endless fun in short bursts, making it perfect for casual play or high-score chasers.', 'Shoot at the right time to match the color', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('running in foam', 2696, 'In the game, we need to control the girl and use various bathing tools to bathe the girl. When the girl successfully washes up and reaches the end, the game will be won. Come and experience it with me.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Paper Doll Makeover Dress Up', 2697, 'Welcome to Paper Doll Makeover &amp;amp; Dress Up, a doll world where the fashion of DIY paper doll and the fun of a doll dress up game come together. Step into this enchanting dress up game and become the stylist of your very own paper princess. With over 1000 fashion items at your fingertips, including trendy clothing, unique accessories, various hairstyles, and ASMR-inspired makeup, you can let your DIY creativity soar through your cute doll.', 'Transform your paper doll into a fashion icon with your styling skills From elegant outfits to stylish accessories design looks that turn your doll princess into a style queen Each choice you make has a significant impact leading your DIY journey in e', 'English'),
('Galaxy Blaster', 2698, 'Galaxy Blaster is an exciting brick-breaking adventure designed for both kids and adults. Smash through waves of glowing bricks as you advance from one level to the next, each more challenging than the last. Collect valuable points along the way and use them to upgrade your paddle, making it stronger and faster. With its cosmic theme and addictive gameplay, Galaxy Blaster guarantees hours of fun among the stars!', 'Arrow keys to move the paddle', 'English'),
('Rapid Match', 2699, 'Tap, match, and clear the row! In this fast-paced puzzle game where timing and precision matter, you shoot blocks from the bottom to hit the matching ones above. Match them right and boom &amp;mdash; the whole row is gone! But watch out &amp;mdash; your block changes on its own!', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game', 'English'),
('Sort And Style: Back To School', 2700, 'Step into the world of Sort And Style: Back To School, a fun mix of sorting and dress-up games for girls! Organize messy desks, lockers, wardrobes, and even bento boxes across 9 exciting levels. Then, challenge your creativity in the final dress-up unit where you style your school look with trendy uniforms, shoes, hairstyles, and accessories. Perfect for fans of organizing games, makeover fun, and school fashion challenges!', 'Use your mouse to play the game on a desktop tap to play on mobile devices', 'English'),
('Fruits Mania', 2701, 'Fruit Mania is a colorful match &amp;amp; tap puzzle game for all ages. Your mission is to help the cute little lemming collect the right fruits! On the board, you&amp;rsquo;ll see plenty of smiling fruit blocks (red strawberries, blue blueberries, yellow lemons, green watermelons, and more). The player must tap groups of same-colored fruits to clear them and earn points. The larger the group of fruits you tap, the higher your score and combo bonus! At the bottom right, the game shows the fruit needed (for example, a red strawberry) that you must collect to complete the level&amp;rsquo;s goal.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Battle SWAT vs Mercenary Remaster', 2702, 'Battle SWAT vs Mercenary throws you into intense first-person shooter action where you pick a side and fight for dominance. Choose to fight as a skilled SWAT soldier or a ruthless mercenary in thrilling multiplayer battles. The game also features a zombie mode, where you can rise from the dead and hunt down your enemies. With fast-paced combat and diverse modes, every match is packed with adrenaline and chaos. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.crazygamesx.com/.''&gt;https://www.crazygamesx.com/.&lt;/a&gt; Mouse to aim, shooting, change gun, Tab for menu, WASD to walk-run.', 'Mouse to aim shooting change gun Tab for menu WASD to walk-run', 'English'),
('Hop To Rescue', 2703, 'Hop To Rescue is a fun and challenging platformer adventure where you help the hero rescue animals trapped in cages. Jump across platforms, avoid traps, and time your moves to clear each level. Collect coins to boost your score and unlock tougher challenges. With smooth one-tap or key controls, colorful 2D graphics, and addictive gameplay, this arcade-style rescue game is easy to play but hard to master. Perfect for fans of action, adventure, and platform games, Hop To Rescue offers endless fun on both desktop and mobile. Play free online and test your skills today!', 'Desktop Press Space or Up Arrow to Jump Mobile Tap anywhere on the screen to Jump', 'English'),
('Cheez Pizza Ready', 2704, 'Cheez Pizza Ready game where you manage and expand your own pizza restaurant, taking orders at the counter and drive-thru, cooking and serving pizzas, managing staff, and growing your business into a chain. The game features a casual, free-to-play experience focused on the business management aspects of running a pizzeria!!', 'Pizza Ready is a simulation game and as such its controlled using touch and tap inputs on your device rather than traditional keyboard or mouse controls Youll simply tap on the screen to interact with your restaurant hire staff manage orders and u', 'English'),
('Number Nexus', 2705, 'Enter the Number Nexus, a world where logic and quick thinking collide! Numbered boxes fall from above, and it&amp;rsquo;s your job to place them wisely. When two blocks of the same value meet, they merge into a single higher number, freeing up space and boosting your score. Every move matters: stack carefully, chain your merges, and keep the board clear while chasing ever-larger numbers. The more you combine, the higher your score climbs&amp;mdash;and the closer you get to mastering the nexus of numbers. With endless possibilities and addictive gameplay, Number Nexus is the perfect test of strategy, foresight, and mathematical mastery. Make your mark!', 'Click to drop the number in that lane', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Superbrain', 2706, 'Run forward and increase the brain in size, you will need it at the end to launch the monkey to another planet. Try to get the maximum brain size.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Cowboy Shooter 2', 2707, 'Step into the Wild West and test your aim in this fast-paced cowboy shooting game! Time is running out, and every shot counts. Break bottles, hit targets, and push yourself to earn the highest score before the clock runs out. With changing weather conditions and an increasingly fast-paced tempo, the excitement rises even higher. With its simple yet addictive gameplay, Cowboy Shooter 2 offers endless fun and a true test of your reflexes. Are you quick enough to become the ultimate sharpshooter?', 'Aim Move the mouse to aim at the targets Shoot Press the Left Mouse Button to fire Mobile Use the on-screen buttons to aim and shoot just like on PC', 'English'),
('Long nails', 2708, 'All we need to do is move the mouse so that the character moves left and right, and then get resources on the field. All we have to do is increase the length of the nails to get to the finish line and get the maximum reward.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Mosaic Master', 2709, 'Unleash your creativity and sharpen your mind in Mosaic Master, a relaxing yet challenging puzzle game where every shape finds its perfect place. How to Play: Fit colorful geometric pieces into beautifully designed patterns. Complete each mosaic to reveal stunning artwork made of soothing colors, flowers, and leaves. Features: Hundreds of Unique Puzzles &amp;ndash; From simple shapes to intricate masterpieces. Relaxing Gameplay &amp;ndash; No timers, just calming music and beautiful visuals. Soothing Aesthetic &amp;ndash; Floral themes and gentle colors for a peaceful experience. Brain Training &amp;ndash; Improve focus, logic, and spatial reasoning.', 'Match the shapes and colors', 'English'),
('Labubu Geometry Dash', 2710, 'Labubu Geometry dash is an avoider game. Play as tiny plane, avoid any obstacles, gain power up and enjoy Labubu dancing. Challenge all 40 level of chaotic level!', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Whimsy Workshop', 2711, 'Step inside the Whimsy Workshop, a playful world where every toy follows the rules of physics&amp;mdash;and sometimes breaks them in surprising ways! Stack, topple, bounce, and roll your way through fun challenges as you experiment with blocks, balls, cars, and more. With realistic physics and endless possibilities, no two play sessions are ever the same. Build towering creations, set up chain reactions, or just enjoy the delightful chaos when everything comes crashing down. Perfect for players of all ages, Whimsy Workshop is a sandbox of creativity, curiosity, and toybox fun. Are you ready to play, build, and discover the magic of physics-driven to', 'Use Mouse Touch to place the objects', 'English'),
('hexa master', 2712, 'Hexa Master Dive into the colorful world of Hexa Master, a dazzling hexagonal match-puzzle game that&amp;rsquo;s perfect for your next gaming fix! Rotate clusters of glowing dots, match three or more, and unleash chain reactions to clear each level. Hundreds of Levels &amp;ndash; Every stage brings new challenges and surprises. Vibrant Visuals &amp;ndash; Stunning graphics and smooth animations make the gameplay a treat for the eyes. Easy to Learn, Hard to Master &amp;ndash; Tap or click to rotate the hexagon; plan moves to get higher scores and bonuses. Relax or Compete &amp;ndash; Play to unwind, or sharpen your strategy to beat your high score. thanks for playing', 'mouse', 'English'),
('Color Connect Master', 2713, 'Color Connect Master Welcome to Color Connect Master, the ultimate puzzle game where colors meet your logic skills! Relax, strategize, and connect your way through dozens of mindteasing levels. Perfect for players of all ages who love a satisfying challenge. How to Play- Connect matching colored dots by drawing continuous lines between them. Ensure that no two lines intersect &amp;mdash; paths must not cross or overlap. Fill the entire grid to complete each level. Features Hundreds of levels with increasing difficulty &amp;mdash; start easy, get challenging! Multiple grid sizes to test your spatial thinking. thanks for playing', 'mouse for pc users', 'English'),
('Rogue Runner', 2714, 'Become the most wanted fugitive in a relentless, high-octane Rogue Runner simulator. Outsmart and outdrive an ever-growing police force in a dynamic open world. Your driving skills are the only thing between freedom and capture. Weave through dense urban traffic, execute dangerous maneuvers, and use the environment to your advantage. Every smashed barrier and near-miss intensifies the pursuit. Feel the adrenaline surge as SWAT teams join the hunt, deploying spike strips and tactical units. How long can you survive with the entire citys law enforcement on your tail? Push your vehicle to its limits, master the streets, and defy capture in', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('The brick', 2715, 'The Brick Smash bricks, collect power-ups, and beat the clock in this high-pace arcade classic! In The Brick, your task is simple but addictive: launch the ball, bounce it off your paddle and destroy every brick on the screen. Grab falling power-ups and extra lives to turn the tide in your favor. Every level brings a fresh challenge&amp;mdash;faster speeds, tight corners, and clever layouts. Keep the ball in play as long as you can; missed catches will cost you lives. Can you keep your reflexes sharp enough to set the ultimate high score? thanks for playing', 'mouse', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Secret Reef Merge', 2716, '**Dive into Sea Merge Drop!** Merge adorable sea animals by dropping matching pairs. Watch them evolve into even cuter creatures! Tap to release animals strategically - create chains of merges for higher scores. Dont let the ocean fill up or its game over! Each merge earns points and unlocks new aquatic friends. Reach level targets to progress through the game. How many merges can you create? How high can you score? Can swim all the way through 10 levels? Simple one-tap gameplay with charming visuals. Perfect for quick play sessions or diving deep into merging madness! Ready to make a splash?', 'Click screen to place sea animals Desktop Tap screen to place sea animals mobile', 'English'),
('Space Stairwell', 2717, 'Space Stairwell is a fast-paced survival game. You control a sphere and must jump up an endless series of platforms rising from the bottom of the screen. The goal is to survive as long as possible by completing levels. Every jump consumes energy, so you must collect items to recharge. The game gets harder in higher levels, with platforms that collapse faster and require quicker reflexes. You can unlock new levels by successfully completing the previous ones.', 'Controls The game can be played on both Mobile and PC Mobile Jump Tap directly on the platform you want to jump to PC Jump Click with your mouse on the platform you want to jump to Slide Use the A D or the Left Right Arrow Keys to slide Smart-J', 'English'),
('Sliding Number Puzzle &amp;ndash; Classic Brain Teaser', 2718, 'Challenge your mind with Sliding Number Puzzle, a timeless brain teaser built with pure HTML5, ready to run seamlessly on desktop and mobile browsers. Rearrange the numbered tiles to restore the correct order in the least number of moves. Perfect for casual gamers and puzzle enthusiasts alike, this game delivers endless replay value with its clean design and addictive gameplay.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('xo for bro', 2719, 'Enjoy the timeless strategy game Tic Tac Toe (XO) with a modern design and smooth animations! Challenge your friends in Player vs Player mode or test your skills against a simple bot. Track your wins, losses, and draws with an automatic score system that saves your progress. With eye-catching visuals, glowing effects, and full mobile support, this version of Tic Tac Toe is the perfect mix of classic gameplay and modern style.', 'Click on any empty cell to place your mark X or O Get 3 in a row horizontally vertically or diagonally to win The game will automatically highlight the winning line or show a draw message', 'English'),
('Scary Baby Pink Horror Game', 2720, 'Welcome to the chilling world of Scary Baby Pink, where babysitting takes on a terrifying twist! Brace yourself for an immersive horror experience unlike any other. Are you ready to face the darkness lurking within Your house. In this spine-tingling game, you play the role of a babysitter tasked with caring for a seemingly innocent baby. However, as night falls, you quickly realize that there is something sinister about the child youre watching over. Your objective? Survive the night and uncover the dark secrets hidden within the babys room while taking care of the baby and keeping her safe from the evil racoon.', '-Arrow keys WASD to move Hold LMB RMB to move the camera to look around and Mouse click to interact for PC users -Touch Screen for mobile users to move and interact in gameplay', 'English'),
('Interactive Jigsaw Puzzle Game', 2721, 'Engage your users with a fun and interactive Jigsaw Puzzle Game built with pure HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript. This fully responsive game allows players to click or tap puzzle pieces, complete puzzles of different sizes, and enjoy a smooth, user-friendly experience. Perfect for websites, educational platforms, or entertainment apps, this game is easy to integrate and customize. Features include multiple puzzle sets, responsive design, timer &amp;amp; move counter, and attractive animations to enhance gameplay.', 'Drag amp drop puzzle pieces', 'English'),
('Dark Spirit Run', 2722, 'Dark Spirit Run Run fast. Dodge death. Embrace the shadows. Step into the shadows as a lone ninja sprinting through a cursed world filled with deadly traps and haunted threats. In Dark Spirit Run, your mission is simple: survive. Swiftly dodge flaming hazards, spinning metal blades, and ghostly spirits as you race through an endless night of danger. One wrong move, and its the end. But with sharp reflexes and a fearless heart, you might just go farther than anyone else.', 'Use Arrow Keys', 'English'),
('Doll Game DIY Fashion Star', 2723, 'Welcome to DIY Fashion Star, a casual DIY simulator game for girls who love fashion clothes and dressing. You need to meet customers needs and offer them your tailored clothes! Use your sense of fashion and beauty to create the best and suitable garments for every client. From selecting cloth formats to cutting and sewing, you witness how a piece of cloth transforms into a beautiful suit.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Reveal the Animal', 2724, 'Reveal the Animal is a fun and educational math game where players must select fractions that add up to 1. As players correctly solve the fraction equations, they will gradually uncover a hidden animal. The game features a variety of animals and difficulty levels, making it suitable for players of all ages.', 'Click to select the fractions', 'English'),
('FNF Girlfriend Multiverse Fashion', 2725, 'Welcome to FNF Girlfriend Multiverse Fashion. Friday Night Funkin&amp;rsquo; Girl seems bored of trying music. She has a plan for something different other than music. Yes, she wants to try multiverse fashion! Sounds fun! right? Join and pick a different fashion outfit. At each level, her wardrobe is filled with different costumes. Help them to choose the best one!', 'Left Mouse Button Click', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Contagion Clash', 2726, 'Strategize your taps and unleash chain reactions in Microbes! The play area is swarming with microbes&amp;mdash;some can shoot, others can&amp;rsquo;t. Your goal is to touch the right microbes in the right order, triggering shots that wipe out all the non-shooters. Plan your moves carefully, because one wrong touch could break the chain! Think smart, tap wisely, and cleanse the petri dish in this infectious puzzle challenge!', 'Plan Think and Play', 'English'),
('Easy Coloring Kitty', 2727, 'Easy Coloring Kitty is a super fun and relaxing coloring game made just for kids. Get ready to bring cute kittens to life with bright colors and silly designs. Pick a picture, grab your favorite shades, and start painting. There is no right or wrong way to play: just have fun, be creative, and let your imagination run wild. Whether you like rainbow cats or classic fluffy friends, this game is all about smiles and color. Perfect for young artists who love animals and fun art time. Coloring has never been this easy or this cute!', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Piercing Skies', 2728, 'Dodge, jump, and survive under a sky of danger in Piercing Skies! Arrows rain down from above as you leap between three narrow platforms, timing each jump to avoid getting struck. Quick reflexes and sharp focus are your only defense in this fast-paced survival challenge. Every second you last adds to your score&amp;mdash;but one mistake, and its game over. Can you outlast the storm and master the art of survival beneath the piercing skies?', 'Move the block to not let the arrows hit it', 'English'),
('Hummer Lady Queen', 2729, 'Hummer Lady Queen is a thrilling luck-based driving game where a bold lady takes control of a powerful hummer and smashes through boxes blocking her path! Each box holds a surprise &amp;mdash; hit the right ones to collect money and boost your fortune, but beware: some contain danger and will cost you a life. Its a high-speed game of risk and reward, where timing, courage, and luck decide your fate. With vibrant visuals, stylish character customization, and unpredictable gameplay, every run is a new challenge. Can you stay alive, get rich, and rule the road like a true queen?', 'Use up and left or right arrow key to play game or touch screen of mobile', 'English'),
('Jelly Connect', 2730, 'Jelly Connect challenges players to pair identical, squishy jellies using a path of no more than three lines. Clear the board quickly to advance. As you progress, each level becomes tougher, requiring sharper memory and strategy. The vibrant visuals and engaging puzzles make it an addictive experience for everyone.', 'Use your mouse or touchscreen to select and connect matching jellies Paths can have up to three straight lines Complete all matches within the time limit to clear the level For faster completion plan your connections ahead', 'English'),
('WW2 Frontline Defense', 2731, 'WW2 Frontline Defense is an idle war strategy game set during World War II. Command machine gunners defending the frontline wall against endless enemy waves. With each wave, enemies grow stronger, faster, and harder to stop. Upgrade your tower, boost game speed, activate artillery strikes, and double your income with powerful bonuses. Build an impenetrable defense and hold the line for as long as possible. Key features: Fast-paced base defense during World War II Tower upgrades and income multipliers Free and premium bonuses (artillery, x2, speed boost) Cloud saves and leaderboards 14 supported languages Play instantly in your browser', 'Enemies attack in waves - hold the line Your tower shoots automatically Earn gold for each enemy killed Upgrade the tower use bonuses speed artillery x2 income Survive as long as you can and beat your score After defeat start over with stronger', 'English'),
('GeometryJump', 2732, 'Control blocks to jump forward on high platforms. Long jump with short jump, there will be a jagged chase behind, speed up the jump, avoid being defeated by the jagged, come to experience it, see how many points you can get.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Speedboa Warer Shooting', 2733, 'Have you ever wanted to drive the fastest speedboat? Feel the stunt and thrill of high-speed rowing! Enjoy a nervous racing game in the Speedboat: Water Shooting. Youll pilot a speedboat in an exciting battle against the enemy in rough seas. Shoot the enemies with your gun. Feel the rush as you race at full speed across the ocean. Aim enemies, blast enemy boats out of your way, and protect yourself!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Merge Master: Weapons Craft', 2734, 'Merge Master: Weapons Craft is a fun and addictive game where you become the ultimate weapon crafter! Start with basic tools and merge them together to create powerful swords, axes, and legendary weapons. Every merge unlocks stronger gear, helping you defeat tougher enemies and bosses. Upgrade your forge, expand your arsenal, and climb the ranks to become the master of weapon crafting. Easy to play, satisfying to merge, and full of action &amp;ndash; build your weapon empire today and show the world your forging skills!', 'Click with mouse or Touch with your phone', 'English'),
('Cube Speed Dash', 2735, 'Jump, dash, and survive in Cube Speed Dash, a high-speed arcade challenge where every second counts! Master lightning-fast reflexes as you guide a nimble cube through treacherous obstacle courses filled with spikes, traps, and deadly pitfalls. One wrong move&amp;mdash;and it&amp;rsquo;s game over! Blazing-Fast Gameplay &amp;ndash; Sprint through short but intense levels designed for quick, addictive sessions. Precision Controls &amp;ndash; Simple tap-and-hold mechanics, but razor-sharp timing is key to victory. Minimalist &amp;amp; Stylish &amp;ndash; Clean neon visuals and smooth animations keep you focused on the action.', 'A Move Left D Move Right Space Jump', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Puzzledom One Line', 2736, 'Welcome to Puzzledom: One Line - the ultimate brain teaser you can&amp;rsquo;t stop drawing. This casual puzzle minigame looks simple, but each level is challenging. There are six ways to play here for you to choose from. For example, draw lines to help boys and girls find the proper toilet to prevent them from colliding.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Build A Queen 2025', 2737, 'In Build a Queen 2025, you will embark on a fun journey to become a real queen. You will need to make your way through different platform levels with your opponents. Choose outfits, skin colors, and more according to your goals. Dress up in the most glamorous queen look, meet the prince, and win. You can collect money to unlock more dance steps.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Redball Avengers', 2738, 'Evil minions want to squeeze the planet into a square shape. Whos got the heroballs to save the world ? Oh yeah, thats right! Be the avenger Hero to the rescue and defeat all the evil squares in this HeroBall adventure! Heroball has shown up to save the world. Collect stars and unlock new characters as AmericaBall, SpiderBall, and Ironball and save the world from the minions.', 'Use the keyboard to play', 'English'),
('Legends John Wicked', 2739, 'John has been urgently called to duty, but a mistake he made during the mission has put him in a dangerous situation. John Wicked is furious &amp;mdash; he&amp;rsquo;s armed himself with all his weapons and is ready for battle. Shoot all the bad guys who stand in your way and reach your car. Get in and escape the scene. The enemies are everywhere, and there are too many of them. Take them down one by one.', 'Use the WASD keys to move Shoot and defeat all incoming enemies Reach your car safely Playable on both mobile and PC', 'English'),
('Blocks Stack Rush', 2740, 'Enjoy an addictive stacking adventure. In Blocks Stack Rush, you&amp;rsquo;ll control a little block character running and begin a fun pixelated journey. Collect blocks, stack them high and race against time to build the perfect picture. You need to align each block and keep putting together the complete picture.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('DownHill Ball', 2741, 'Downhill Ride challenges players to control a constantly descending ball as it navigates through tricky obstacles. Players need quick reflexes to avoid crashing while the games pace escalates. With an addictive, endless runner style, you must stay focused to travel as far as possible without colliding.', 'Use simple controls tap to move the ball left or right Your goal is to bypass obstacles and keep the ball rolling As you progress speed increases demanding sharper reflexes A helpful hint plan your moves ahead of time to dodge impending challenges', 'English'),
('Dirty Home Cleaning Fix', 2742, 'Are you a storing master? Do you always get annoyed at tidying up? Or do you feel confused about what to start with in front of a messy room? This casual cleaning girl game - Dirty Home Cleaning Fix will give solutions to all your questions! Use your wit and patience to put the messy room in order.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Brainrot Rescue', 2743, 'Brainrot Rescue is a festive puzzle game where players help Brainrot Claus retrieve his stolen gifts from mischievous snowmen. The gameplay revolves around strategically pulling pins to guide Santa safely through various obstacles, such as hot lava and icy traps, to collect presents and defeat enemies. With 30 challenging levels, players must use problem-solving skills to determine the correct sequence of pin pulls, ensuring Brainrot safe passage and the successful recovery of all gifts.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Minecraft lava chicken 2', 2744, 'Minecraft Chicken Lava 2 is a fun and fiery spotting challenge where your mission is simple&amp;mdash;but intense: find and grab all the lava chickens hidden in each picture! These glowing, molten chickens blend into the lava-filled Minecraft landscapes, and it&amp;rsquo;s up to you to spot them all before time runs out. Each level features: Detailed Minecraft Scenes &amp;ndash; Full of lava lakes, obsidian blocks, and sneaky hiding spots. Lava Chickens &amp;ndash; Unique chickens with a fiery glow, hidden in plain sight.', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Silent Shuriken', 2745, 'Step into the shadows and test your reflexes in Silent Shuriken! As a swift and silent ninja, you must dodge deadly blades, spinning traps, and slicing hazards that threaten to cut you down at every turn. Collect bonus objects scattered across the battlefield to boost your score, but stay alert&amp;mdash;one wrong move and it&amp;rsquo;s all over. Only the sharpest reflexes and stealthiest moves will keep you alive in this deadly dance of steel!', 'Click to go to other side be careful to collect only fruits', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Blade n Vines', 2746, 'Blade &amp;amp; Vines is an action-packed Amazonian battle adventure where nature itself becomes your greatest weapon! As a fierce warrior of the jungle, you must harness the power of enchanted vines and razor-sharp blades to defeat waves of enemies standing in your way. Use your unique abilities&amp;mdash;whip enemies with thorned vines, summon towering roots to block attacks, and unleash devastating blade combos to carve your path to victory. With every battle won, your powers grow stronger, unlocking new skills and strategies to dominate the jungle battlefield.', 'Keep playing', 'English'),
('BouncingBall', 2747, 'Control the character through the ring. Avoid touching the edge of the ring, there will be some sharp traps during the movement, avoid touching the trap.Come and experience it.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Commando Shooting', 2748, 'Commando Shooter is an intense top-down military action game where you step into the boots of an elite soldier fighting against waves of enemies. Navigate through hostile territory, collect powerful weapons, and eliminate enemy forces in this adrenaline-pumping arcade shooter! Key Features: Fast-paced combat action with intuitive touch/mouse controls Multiple weapon systems to collect and master - from rapid-fire machine guns to devastating rocket launchers Progressive difficulty across numerous challenging levels and sectors Epic boss battles against armored vehicles, bunkers, and gunner emplacements Upgrade system to enhance your weapons,', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Car Dealer Idle', 2749, 'Ever dreamed of becoming a top Car Dealer? In Car Dealer Idle, you&amp;rsquo;ll manage your own vehicle business. Buy and sell cars, expand your showroom, and grow into a real tycoon. Make smart management decisions, upgrade your dealership, and watch your profits skyrocket. Unlock more booths to sell cooler vehicles. Unlock repair areas, test drive areas, etc.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Shark Tralalero Tralala', 2750, 'Shark Tralalero Tralala is a casual arcade game about the meme Tralalelo Tralala. Play as a shark and help it find sneakers! Shark Tralalero Tralala is a casual arcade game consisting of 30 levels. Play as a shark, an Italian meme brain-mouth animal, also known as Tralalelo Tralala. Help the shark find sneakers underwater, avoiding obstacles and aggressive fish!', 'The PC version of the game is controlled by the AD keys or arrow keys larr rarr The mobile version is controlled by on-screen buttons', 'English'),
('Surprise Birthday Party', 2751, 'What can you recall in terms of the birthday party? Do you want to leave a favorite ever birthday memory? Welcome to the Surprise Birthday Party! Here is a collection of mini-games related to birthday parties, including cake cooking, dressing up, wrapping gifts, and arranging a birthday party feast! You do not want to miss any of the celebration sessions! Join and make this casual game your cozy party escape.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki Memory Time', 2752, 'Sprunki Memory Time is a fun and free online game made just for kids. Your goal is to find all the matching cards. Flip the cards one by one and remember where each picture is. When you find two that match, they disappear. Keep going until you clear the board and move on to the next level. Each level gets a little trickier, so get ready to train your memory and have lots of fun. Sprunki Memory Time is a great game to play anytime you want to relax, learn, and enjoy. Try it now and see how many levels you can finish!', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Slice And Solve', 2753, 'Slice &amp;amp; Solve is a fun and interactive math puzzle game that challenges you to master fractions! Slice objects into equal parts and solve fraction-based puzzles to progress through exciting levels. Whether youre learning fractions or sharpening your math skills, Slice &amp;amp; Solve makes learning both engaging and enjoyable. With increasing difficulty and clever challenges, this game is perfect for players of all ages. Can you slice your way to victory? Play now and become a fraction-solving pro!', 'Fraction you better know', 'English'),
('Stick Up!', 2754, 'Let Stickman rise up high and escape from dangers and obstacles.Protect stick from swords, saws, razors and shurikens with your shield and hit new records! Clean the way with shield and reach clouds in this escape rise up game. Touch the shield and protect the ballon or the stickman will fall, collect diamonds and make up your stickman friend', 'Mouse or Touch for play', 'English'),
('Brainrot sahuuur', 2755, 'Are you brairot enough to survive this absurd meme quiz? Step into the world of chaotic Italian memes, pure nonsense, and 100% cooked brain cells. Each question makes less sense than the last &amp;mdash; and that&amp;rsquo;s the point. Features: Completely illogical, intentionally dumb questions Viral meme sounds and cursed images Hilarious answers that defy reason A final test to measure your true brairot level', 'mouse click', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Fruit Pop it', 2756, 'Fruit Pop It challenges players to match and burst colorful fruit bubbles to clear each level. This addictively fun game offers a delightful mix of excitement and relaxation, with charming visuals and upbeat sounds. Conquer numerous levels and enjoy the gratifying popping sensation. Perfect for puzzle enthusiasts of all ages!', 'Tap and drag to swap adjacent fruit bubbles Match three or more of the same to pop them Advance through levels by meeting specific goals or clearing the board Race against the clock or take time for strategy Hint Create combos to earn extra points a', 'English'),
('Crazy Parking Jam  Car Jam Game', 2757, 'Parking Jam is a challenging puzzle game where you untangle a crowded parking lot one car at a time. Use your logic and problem-solving skills to move vehicles in the correct order, clearing the way without causing chaos. With each level, tackle increasingly complex puzzles filled with more cars and tricky obstacles. How to Play Parking Jam Everyones been stuck in a parking jam, but the real challenge is figuring out how to escape! This is a satisfying puzzle game where you click and drag cars to clear them from a crowded parking lot and onto the street.', 'Click and slightly drag the cars in the direction you want them to get out of the parking lot', 'English'),
('Extreme Mega Ramp Car Stunts', 2758, 'Get ready for the ultimate stunt-driving challenge in Mega Ramp Car Stunts! Take control of powerful cars and race down sky-high mega ramps to perform mind-blowing jumps, flips, and tricks. Defy gravity as you soar through the air and land like a pro on impossible tracks. With dynamic gameplay, extreme stunts, and intense visuals, this is the stunt arena where only the boldest drivers survive!', 'WASD or Arrow Keys', 'English'),
('Rainbow Frontline', 2759, 'Rainbow Frontline is a fast-paced 2D pixel shooter set in a vibrant rainbow galaxy under siege! Take control of a retro spaceship, dodge falling meteors, and blast colorful alien enemies in wave-based battles. Master each levels theme&amp;mdash;from red to violet&amp;mdash;as you fight through the spectrum! You can upgrade your ship using collected coins to gain - Extra lives - Timed shield invincibility - Powerful damage boosts Core Features: *Rainbow-themed stages with unique enemies *Colorful boss fights and endless meteors *Rewarded ads for bonus coins *Simple, intuitive controls &amp;mdash; tap and fly *Track your high scores and survival', 'Control For Keyboard Arrow keys or WASD rarr Direction Control Space Key rarr Fire Control For Mobile Virtual Joystick Control', 'English'),
('TempleEscape', 2760, 'Control the character to avoid being chased by giant spheres and avoid various traps. During the game you can get gold, gold can be used to buy a variety of cool character skins, the game is endless gameplay, quick to see how many points you can achieve.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Pengu Pengu', 2761, 'Hurry up, Pengu, and collect all the fish! The penguins are very hungry and its getting harder to find food. Gather every fish and make your way to the mother penguin. Be careful &amp;mdash; polar bears and dangerous traps are everywhere. Avoid the deadly traps and reach the mother penguin and her egg. Don&amp;rsquo;t forget: collect all the fish!', 'You can move using the WASD keys Mobile controls are available Collect all the fish in the level and reach the mother penguin and her egg', 'English'),
('Minecraft Lava Chicken', 2762, 'Minecraft Lava Chicken is a fun, fast-paced hidden object game set in the pixelated world of Minecraft, where your mission is simple yet addictive: find all 10 Lava Chickens hidden in each stage before time runs out! In this unique twist on the classic find the hidden object formula, players dive into rich, colorful Minecraft-inspired scenes&amp;mdash;dense forests, deep caves, bustling villages, and even the fiery Nether. Each stage is a handcrafted Minecraft image,', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Zombie Shooting King', 2763, 'The apocalypse is here! Hordes of zombies are swarming the streets. You are the last line of defense. Grab your gun, sharpen your shooting skills, and unleash unstoppable firepower to survive. Shoot fuel tanks, airdrops, and more to get more firepower to destroy tons of zombies. Get diamonds to upgrade your talents like Guardrail, ATK Boost, Crit Rate, or Coin earning!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Dudu Engineering Truck', 2764, 'DuDu Engineering Truck is a casual and puzzle game where you drive engineering trucks to finish tasks on the worksite. Use your sensitivity to shapes to construct a truck and conquer all challenges ahead. If you love car designing and car games, never miss DuDu Engineering Truck! You will enjoy an adventurous journey of being an engineer.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Ultrahero Vs Monsters Royale Battle', 2765, 'Ultrahero Vs Monsters Royale Battle is an action fighting game where you, as a mighty Ultrahero. Battle against waves of evil monsters in a 3D world. Every battle is a new adventure. Feel the perfect fusion of tower defense and nervous arcade action in this game. As a hero, you must not only fight off monsters in epic battles but also use tower defense tactics to protect your base.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Balloon Boom', 2766, 'Balloon Boom is an exciting color-matching arcade game where quick reflexes are the key to success! Use your colored pin to pop only the balloons that match. Each correct pop earns you points, but one wrong tap and it&amp;rsquo;s game over! The speed increases as you go, keeping the challenge alive. With bright visuals, smooth animations, and simple one-tap controls, Balloon Boom is perfect for players of all ages. How long can you survive the popping frenzy?', 'Desktop Click on the left button of the balloon that matches your pin color Mobile Tap the matching-colored balloon on the screen', 'English'),
('Summer Runway Challenge', 2767, 'Get ready to shine under the sun in Summer Runway Challenge, the ultimate fashion dress-up game! Show off your style by dressing models in the latest summer trends and sending them down the runway. With vibrant outfits, makeup choices, and accessories, this game is perfect for fashion lovers who want to create the perfect summer look.', 'Left Mouse Button Click or Tap to Play', 'English'),
('Dino run run', 2768, 'Experience the classic thrill of the Chrome offline dinosaur game &amp;mdash; now with a fresh new twist! Dino Run Run is a fast-paced endless runner where you dodge obstacles and rack up your high score in a minimalist desert landscape. Whether youre online or offline, the adventure never stops!', 'Computer Use the Up and Down arrow keys to jump and duck Touch Screens Swipe up to jump and swipe down to duck', 'English'),
('PopPopPop', 2769, 'Control the ball safely to the end. There will be many roads on the way to the end, and the ball needs to be timed to safely enter each road.Come and experience it.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Turbo Tables', 2770, 'Turbo Tables is a fast-paced and exciting math game that puts your multiplication skills to the test! Race against the clock to solve multiplication problems quickly and accurately, earning points for speed and precision. With increasing difficulty levels, power-ups, and a thrilling time challenge, Turbo Tables makes learning times tables fun and engaging for players of all ages. Sharpen your math skills, boost your reflexes, and become a multiplication master! Are you fast enough to conquer the tables? Play now and find out!', 'Learn the tables right', 'English'),
('Hidden Object Farm Adventure', 2771, 'Play a fun hidden object game with 30 farm levels!\\\\\\\\nIn each level, find 6 hidden things before time runs out. If you need help, use a hint! Its easy to play and full of colorful farm fun.', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game', 'English'),
('Word Tangle', 2772, 'Word Tangle is a fun and brain-teasing word puzzle game where you unscramble mixed-up letters to form the correct words! Challenge your vocabulary, spelling, and problem-solving skills as you work through exciting levels with scrambled words of varying difficulty. Perfect for word game lovers of all ages, Word Tangle keeps your mind sharp and entertained. Can you untangle all the words and become a true word master? Play now and put your skills to the test!', 'Complete the words', 'English'),
('CarRunner', 2773, 'It is very important to control the safe turning of a car on the road and grasp the right timing. If the timing is wrong, it is very easy to hit the rocks by the roadside and fail. You can get coin rewards during the cars movement. The coins can be used to purchase other exquisite cars. Come and give it a try. Its very exciting and fun.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Ghost Jump', 2774, 'Ghost Jump has you navigating a maze as a ghost leaping through colorful challenges. Each jump tests your timing and reflexes, as you adapt to new obstacles. Quick reactions are essential to maintain your streak, making each moment a thrilling challenge in this endlessly entertaining experience.', 'Tap the screen to propel your ghost Align the ghosts color with the barriers to progress Begin with basic challenges and advance to harder stages Mistakes mean starting over Helpful hint Prioritize timing to gradually master the gameplay', 'English'),
('Brainrot Clicker Game', 2775, 'Italian Brainrot Clicker &amp;ndash; Tap to earn, laugh to survive! In this absurd HTML5 clicker game, you&amp;rsquo;ll meet the weirdest cast ever: sharks with shoes, chocolate blocks with bats, birds with bellies, and more. Your goal? Tap on them as fast as you can to gain points, trigger animations, and unlock total chaos. Simple click-to-play gameplay Packed with meme-fueled Italian brainrot characters Colorful 2D cartoon style and silly effects Runs directly in your browser &amp;ndash; no downloads needed Play now and join the madness! Only the fastest fingers will survive.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Hidden Totals', 2776, 'Hidden Totals is a fun and engaging counting game where you test your observation skills by finding how many times a specific object appears in a given image! Look closely, count carefully, and tap the correct total to score points. With increasing difficulty across multiple levels, this game challenges your focus, memory, and quick thinking. Perfect for kids and adults alike, Hidden Totals is a great way to sharpen your counting skills while having fun. Can you spot them all? Play now and put your eyes to the test!', 'Count amp Write', 'English'),
('World Flag Quiz', 2777, 'World Flag Quiz is a fast-paced, fun, and educational mobile game that challenges players to match countries with their correct flags. Designed with simplicity and clarity in mind, the game offers a single, highly addictive game mode that tests your geographical knowledge one country at a time. In each round, players are presented with the name of a country &amp;mdash; such as France, Brazil, Japan, or Nigeria &amp;mdash; and must choose the correct flag from a set of four options. Only one is right, and the other three are cleverly selected to test your attention to detail and flag recognition skills.', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Tung Tung Sahur Big Stick', 2778, 'You must help Tung Tung Sahur and guide him to reach his favorite and most powerful stick. Together with Tung Tung Sahur, jump over all the obstacles in the city, avoid every trap, and reach the end of the level safely to claim the mighty stick. Sometimes you&amp;rsquo;ll become a superhero, and other times a ninja. Join Tung Tung Sahur on his dangerous adventure through the city and help him succeed.', 'Use the WASD keys to move Collect all the Tung Tung coins and reach the mighty stick 4 different costumes are available in the shop You must reach the end of the level safely', 'English'),
('Extreme Car City Driving', 2779, 'Meet the ultimate driving challenge. In Extreme Car City Driving, you drive a cool car through an open city. Your goal is simple: Drive, explore, and push the limits to become the ultimate racer! Experience a realistic 3D urban environment with full freedom to roam and drive. Enjoy free driving and complete various driving tasks. Such as fixed-point parking, top speed racing, extreme drifting and so on, testing your driving skills!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Banana Quest', 2780, 'Get ready for a thrilling jungle adventure in Banana Quest! Play as a brave monkey on a mission to collect as many bananas as possible while dodging spikes, jumping over obstacles, and avoiding enemies. With vibrant graphics, catchy music, and smooth controls, this endless runner offers nonstop action and excitement. The more bananas you collect, the higher your score climbs! Perfect for players of all ages&amp;mdash;simple to play, hard to master!', 'Desktop Press the left button of the mouse to jump the Monkey Mobile Tap the screen to jump the Monkey', 'English'),
('Agent Hunt Shoot', 2781, 'You play the role of an elite agent and are locked in a nervous battle. Enter the Agent Hunt Shoot, grab a powerful weapon in your hand and destroy your enemies with precision shooting! Hide behind the crates to cover yourself and hunt down the enemies. Winning selects higher damage guns, bombs, helmets, etc.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Gun Rush', 2782, 'Begin an action-packed gun battle runner. Gun Rush is an electrifying arcade game that combines gun merging with platform running. Run forward, avoid obstacles, collect weapons, and blast your way to the finish line with ultimate firepower. Control the direction of your gun, shooting power, ATK speed, and Range to increase its value. Increase your damage by using high-value doors.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Pale Pursuit', 2783, 'Run fast, jump high, and don&amp;rsquo;t look back in Pale Pursuit! Haunted by relentless ghostly figures, you must leap over enemy spirits and deadly traps to stay alive. The pace never slows and the phantoms never stop&amp;mdash;only your reflexes can keep you ahead. Precision and timing are your only tools in this eerie, fast-paced survival chase. How long can you outrun the pale shadows of the night?', 'Click to jump', 'English'),
('Sprunki Mega Punch', 2784, 'Sprunki Mega Punch - a casual arcade game where a red sprunki named Reddy decided to show his mega punch! Help him to hit the sprunki of the Tree. Sprunki Mega Punch is a causal reflex arcade game where you need to show sleight of hand and help sprunki Reddys fist reach the target, or rather, the sprunki Tree. The game has 24 levels to complete and 6 skins for Reddy!', 'Control on a PC WS or uarr darr On a mobile device - using on-screen buttons The goal of the game playing as a fist you need to avoid obstacles and hit a sprunki Tree', 'English'),
('Gumdrop Blasters', 2785, 'Blast your way through a world of square-shaped candy madness in Gumdrop Blaster! Match and shoot colorful gumdrop bubbles to clear the board in this addictive candy-themed bubble shooter. With each level, the challenge grows as new patterns of sweet square candies descend faster and trickier. Use precise aim and power-ups to create explosive candy combos and clear the screen before it overflows! Colorful gumdrops, satisfying pops, and endless blasting fun await!', 'Match the candies', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Bunny Jumpy', 2786, 'Get ready to jump into fun! In Bunny Jumpy, help a super cute pink bunny bounce on stretchy trampolines, dodge tricky obstacles, and soar through the sky! Tap at the right time to keep jumping higher&amp;mdash;but be careful: trampolines break after 3 jumps! Simple to play, hard to master, and totally adorable. Features: Colorful 2D cartoon graphics Satisfying bounce mechanics Intuitive one-tap controls Perfect for kids and casual players How far can you jump before the trampoline snaps?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Stick Hero Fight', 2787, 'Enter the most nervous stickman battles. In Stick Hero Fight, you as a mighty stickman hero. Fight through waves of enemies using incredible battle skills. This action game lets you upgrade your hero and unleash devastating attacks to dominate every fight! Use punches, weapons, and powerful skills to deliver deadly attacks.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Princess Doll Dress Up Beauty', 2788, 'Welcome to Princess Doll Dress Up Beauty - a casual princess simulation game. Here you can freely create the most beautiful doll in the world. If you are a fashion and beauty lover, you will definitely feel familiar with all the items in the game. From hair design to dress up, from choosing fashionable clothes to matching different accessories, you are a styling master to design a unique fashion character!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('FantasticLandia', 2789, 'Welcome to FantasticLandia, a world full of wonder and excitement! Jump through vibrant landscapes, solve fun challenges, and have endless hours of fun as you explore every corner!', 'wasd space', 'English'),
('Italian Brainrot Coloring Pages', 2790, 'Welcome to the game where you will find 12 different pictures that need to be colored. They need to be colored and for this you are provided with a set of fifteen felt-tip pens of different bright colors. On the left you will see a set of circles of different diameters. You can also save the colored image. Have fun playing this Italian Brainrot Coloring Pages game!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Gemstone Glam', 2791, 'Welcome to the fabulous world filled with sparkling gems! Here you will meet two charming princess girlfriends, Eliza and Tiara, who adore fashionable outfits and the glitter of colorful stones in fashionable outfits. Try on dresses inspired by the radiance of a diamond, the passion of a ruby, the freshness of an emerald and the mystery of an amethyst. Create shining combinations of hairstyles, dresses and accessories to transform our young princesses into real fashion queens. Be inspired by the natural beauty of gems and come up with images worthy of a fairy tale. Feel like a real stylist of the jewelry kingdom!', 'Depending on the gaming device either a click of a computer mouse or a simple touch on touchscreens is used to control it', 'English'),
('Rogue Seas Adventure', 2792, 'Set sail with a fearless straw-hat kid and his rubber-quick reflexes in Rogue Seas Adventure! Hop between tiny islands, rescue captured crewmates, and stack your power before the final clash with the swampy sea-boss. Draw the perfect path, grab hidden treasure chests, and watch your elastic hero&amp;rsquo;s strength skyrocket from 5 &amp;rarr; 9 &amp;rarr; &amp;infin;&amp;mdash;all in snappy, one-minute puzzle rounds. Dream of becoming the next great Pirate King? This is your first step. Gather your crew, sharpen your instincts, and rule the rogue seas!', 'Tap islands to add their numbers to yours mdash stack the biggest total and crush the boss', 'English'),
('BTS Princess Coloring Book', 2793, 'BTS Princess Coloring Book is fun online coloring game for kids. This time you can choose one of the cool princess images and color it the way you like. Have fun!', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Getting Over It Unblocked', 2794, 'Start the most wonderful climbing adventure ever at Getting Over It Unblocked. This game will test your patience, skill, and determination like never before. You play as a man stuck in a giant pot, armed with only a hammer to climb impossible platforms. Your goal is to keep going up. Three different adventures are waiting to challenge you. Note hollowed-out platforms, longer distances, etc.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Driver Run 3D', 2795, 'Begin a wonderful car arcade running game. In the Driver Run 3D, not only do you have to run, but you also have to collect car parts. Assemble your car and race your way to the finish line. As a top racer, you must move flexibly on the platform. Collect wheels, body, engine, and other parts to complete your dream car. But be careful of obstacles.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Cave Crawl', 2796, 'Cave Crawl is an exciting underground adventure where danger lurks at every turn! Step into the boots of a brave explorer and venture deep into mysterious caves filled with traps, treasures, and terrifying creatures. How to play: Tap and swipe to move through narrow tunnels and hidden chambers. Avoid spikes, falling rocks, lava pits, and lurking monsters. Collect gems, ancient artifacts, and power-ups to aid your escape. Each level brings new surprises and increasingly tough challenges. Use your reflexes, timing, and courage to navigate the ever-changing cave system. The deeper you go, the harder it gets&amp;mdash;but the rewards are worth it!', 'key arrow to play', 'English'),
('Astra runner 3d', 2797, 'Bounce your way through a colorful world full of moving platforms, tricky gaps, and endless challenges! Control a ball with simple tap or click mechanics &amp;mdash; jump over obstacles, time your movements perfectly, and aim for the highest score.', 'Use the arrow keys or on-screen buttons to move your character Collect coins and avoid obstacles The game restarts when you lose Try to get the highest score Controls Arrow Keys Touch Buttons ndash Move character Space Tap ndash Jump or per', 'English'),
('Draw Weapon Fight Party', 2798, 'In Draw Weapon - Fight Party, you can draw your own weapons. Feel free to write your weapon, but keep an eye on the amount of ink left. Your creativity determines your combat style. Enter the 3D battle arena and fight against other opponents in an action-packed showdown. Draw precisely, craft the ultimate weapon, and crush your opponents to become the ultimate warrior.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Italian Brainrot Hangman', 2799, 'Your friends tung tung tung sahur, tralaleo tralala, and more need your help to solve these fun, engaging Hangman puzzles! Guess what Italian brainrot character by guessing letters! Will you guess em all, or will the man be the hanged? Find out today by playing our free online Italian brainrot hangman puzzle! Its fun for everyone!', 'Click or tap the letters to solve the Hangman puzzle Can you guess em all', 'English'),
('Flower Jam', 2800, 'Enter Flower Jam is a vibrant casual match game with colorful flowers and exciting puzzles. You aim to complete the level by swapping flowers and eliminating them by getting six petals of the same color! Place petals of the same color together to make six petals to eliminate. Get props to help you eliminate tons of flowers.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Trendy Casual Day Out', 2801, 'Welcome to Trendy Casual Day Out. If you love picking out outfits and matching cute clothes, this game is for you. Trendy Casual Day Out lets you style a character for a relaxed day in town. You can go with jeans and sneakers, or a skirt and a fun top. Just like getting ready in real life, it&amp;rsquo;s all about putting together something that feels right for the day.', 'Left Mouse Button Click or Tap to Play', 'English'),
('Car Care Repair DuDu Mechanic', 2802, 'Car Care Repair DuDu Mechanic is a casual simulation game where you act as a skillful mechanic. Your clients meet diverse problems with their cars: broken windows, cracked car doors, flat tires, malfunctioning motors, lack of car parts...', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Turbo Racer 3D', 2803, 'Get ready to feel the speed in Turbo Racer 3D! This fast-paced 3D racing game combines the best of casual, hyper-casual, and runner genres to deliver a thrilling experience you can enjoy on the go. Dodge traffic, collect nitro boosts, and unlock powerful turbo upgrades as you race through vibrant tracks in high-performance cars. Whether youre a fan of car games, racing, or addictive runner-style gameplay, Turbo Racer 3D will keep your adrenaline pumping.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Chinese Food Chef DuDu', 2804, 'Are you a fan of Chinese food? Do you want to discover the mystery of delicious Chinese cuisine? You do not want to miss this cooking game - Chinese Food Chef DuDu. Here, you have the chance to learn different recipes of traditional Chinese food, such as dumplings, rice dumplings, and zongzi. Win the heart of the little monkey with your delicious Chinese food!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Treasure King Adventure', 2805, 'Embark on a thrilling journey in Treasure King Adventure! Assemble your team of intrepid adventurers and delve into mysterious dungeons filled with untold riches and perilous traps. Navigate treacherous terrain, solve cunning puzzles, and engage in strategic battles to claim the title of the legendary Treasure King. Uncover hidden treasures, unlock powerful artifacts, and conquer formidable foes in this epic quest for glory and wealth. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.coolcrazygames.com/''&gt;https://www.coolcrazygames.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Stylish Hip Hop Girl', 2806, 'Step into the world of urban fashion and street dance with Stylish Hip Hop Girl! This addictive dress-up and rhythm game lets you design fierce outfits, style your character, and show off your best dance moves. Whether you love fashion, hip hop culture, or just fun creative games, this is your chance to express your unique swag!', 'Left Mouse Button Click or Tap to Play', 'English'),
('Jump Redball', 2807, 'A little game made by your familys beloved game developer, where you try to last as long as possible by jumping on platforms without falling on the saws.', 'Just left and right arrow or A and D keys', 'English'),
('Easter Bunny Coloring Book', 2808, 'Coloring Book: Easter Bunny is a fun and free coloring game for all ages! Choose from 16 adorable Easter bunny illustrations and unleash your creativity with over 20 carefully selected colors. Paint, design, and adjust your brush size to create the perfect masterpiece! Enjoy a relaxing, high-definition coloring experience on any device with our touch-friendly controls. Bring these cute bunnies to life with vibrant colors and your unique artistic style. Play now and hop into a world of colorful Easter fun!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Vovan Velocity', 2809, 'Vovan Velocity One jump. One chance. Full speed ahead! In Vovan Velocity, you are Vovan &amp;mdash; a fearless runner trapped in a loop of ever-repeating, ever-deadly obstacles. Your only weapon? Perfect timing. Jump with precision to dodge spikes, traps, and surprise patterns. One misstep and it&amp;rsquo;s game over. Simple to play, tough to master &amp;mdash; this is pure reflex-fueled madness!', 'Click to jump and avoid obstacles', 'English'),
('Knife Master: Agility Arcade', 2810, 'If you want to challenge yourself or just relax playing a satifying game, this is for you.Try to hit all knives on your target to clear each stage. Sharpen your skills and test your accuracy in this fast-paced knife-throwing game! Hit all the targets, time your throws perfectly, and conquer increasingly difficult levels. Unlock and upgrade a variety of unique knives, each with its own style and speed. Use your tomatoes to improve your arsenal and push your high score even further. Compete on the global leaderboard and prove youre the true Knife Master!', 'Touch to throw the knife You lose if the knife hits another knife You must hit the target with all knives to clear a stage Golden knives will remove a stuck knife', 'English'),
('Battle Tung Tung Sahur 2Player', 2811, 'Are you ready for the battle of the Tung Tung Sahurs? Two teams are fighting each other, and the one who reaches the chest wins the game. Get ready to fight alongside your friend. Hit your opponent with the sticks and win the game. The player who stays at the chest the longest will be the winner. To win the game, you must defeat your friend.', 'Use the WASD keys to play Press the S key to hit with the stick Use the Arrow keys to play Press the Down Arrow key to hit with the stick Stay near the chest for 20 seconds to win the game', 'English'),
('Giant Wanted Monster', 2812, 'The city is being occupied by giant monsters. You, as an elite sniper, pick up your sniper gun. Defeat these crazy monsters and protect the survival of humanity. In Giant Wanted Monster, the fate of the city is at stake with every bullet. You need to use the powerful sniper weapon to shoot accurately from a distance and hit the monsters Achilles heel.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Stickman Hero Skibidi Tower Defense', 2813, 'Fight off waves of Skibidi invaders in the Stickman Hero Skibidi Tower Defense. In this casual tower defense puzzle game, take control of the Stickman Hero. Use your strategic skills to build powerful towers and stop the Skibidi army. Move your hero wisely to enhance his power. Expanding his numbers to attack stronger enemies.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Tiny Word Grid&amp;nbsp;', 2814, 'Tiny Word Grid is a fun and engaging crossword game designed to challenge your vocabulary and word skills! Solve exciting word puzzles by filling in the grid with the correct words. Each level presents a unique challenge, from simple words to trickier brain teasers. Whether youre a beginner or a word puzzle expert, Tiny Word Grid offers endless hours of educational and entertaining gameplay. Sharpen your mind, expand your vocabulary, and enjoy solving crosswords anytime, anywhere! Ready to become a word master? Start playing now!', 'Click on empty boxes', 'English'),
('World Conqueror', 2815, 'World Conqueror is an epic strategy game where players step into the shoes of historic leaders, commanding armies and shaping the course of history. From ancient empires to modern conflicts, players navigate through pivotal moments, making critical decisions that determine the fate of nations. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.crazygamesonline.com/''&gt;https://www.crazygamesonline.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Roblox Couple Dress up', 2816, 'Get ready to unleash your creativity with Roblox Couple Dress-up, a fun and exciting fashion game where you can design the perfect outfits for Roblox characters. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re dressing up for a casual day out or a glamorous event, the possibilities are endless. Choose from a variety of trendy clothes, accessories, and hairstyles to style the perfect couple look. Perfect for fashion enthusiasts and Roblox fans alike, this dress-up game brings your virtual fashion dreams to life!', 'Left Mouse Button Click', 'English'),
('Ludo King   offline Ludo Game', 2817, 'Dive into the world of Ludo Super, an all-in-one board game experience featuring Ludo, Bead 16, Tic Tac Toe, and Snakes &amp;amp; Ladders! Connect with friends and family from around the globe, and engage in real-time voice chats for a truly interactive gaming experience. Whether youre a fan of classic board games or looking to make new friends through gaming, Ludo Super has something for everyone.', 'Mouse Controls', 'English'),
('BuildUp 3D', 2818, 'Challenge your mind and test your reflexes in BuildUp 3D &amp;ndash; the ultimate 3D puzzle and tower-building game! Stack blocks perfectly, rise higher with each level, and grow your tower to the skies in this satisfying and addictive casual puzzle game. Perfect for fans of building games, BuildUp 3D combines strategy, timing, and precision in a simple yet endlessly fun experience. Watch your tower grow up as you build in beautiful 3D environments, where one mistake can topple everything!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Silly Quiz', 2819, 'Silliness levels are dropping and the world is in big trouble! Dr. Dimbus needs you to take on the weirdest trivia game ever. Silly Quiz is packed with fun questions, dad jokes, bad puns, and ridiculous challenges. Save the day by surviving this funny quiz where wrong answers might just make things even sillier. If you love funny trivia games, or just causing a little chaos, this one&amp;rsquo;s for you. Warning: side effects may include uncontrollable giggling.', 'Click or tap to choose your answer before the timer runs out Some questions are logical and some are not If you get stuck you can tap the Ask Dr Dimbus button for help Make sure your volume is on to enjoy the music and funny sound effects', 'English'),
('Ocean Orbs', 2820, 'Dive into the deep blue in Ocean Orbs, a mesmerizing underwater adventure! Match the adorable orbs as they float down, and guide them to the correct color zone. With stunning oceanic visuals and tranquil music, Ocean Orbs offers a relaxing yet challenging gameplay experience.', 'Orbs of different colors will float down from the top of the screen Tap the correct orb button at the bottom to match the orb color falling Missing a match will cost you a life You have 5 lives per game Keep matching orbs correctly to score points Th', 'English'),
('Cimb Masters', 2821, 'Accept the challenge and conquer the truest of natures wonders! Tap the screen to climb the rocks but dont miss or you will fall, earn diamonds and buy new characters. Reach the top of all mountains and unlock new exciting levels around the world.', 'Mouse or Touch for play', 'English'),
('Flappy Smoker', 2822, 'It is similar to flappy bird but it has a windows xp wallpaper and our best man XD. Just click the start button and fly more like a bird.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('GunMyTungtungSahur 2Player', 2823, 'The Tung Tung Sahur brothers are very angry. Both of them are furious with each other now. You must help them in their battle together with your friend. Grab a weapon and let the fastest one win. You need to collect the drops falling from the sky. The one who gets hit the most loses the battle. Fight your friend and win this war. Take the drop to get a more powerful weapon.', 'The red player moves using the WASD keys The blue player moves using the arrow keys The one who gets hit 20 times loses', 'English'),
('Idle Landmark Builder', 2824, 'Enjoy a casual idle simulation management game in the Idle Landmark - Builder. Here, youll play the role of a construction tycoon and build world-famous landmarks from scratch. Manage workers to increase speed or your income, hire more workers and build your own construction empire. Build world-famous landmarks such as the Eiffel Tower and the Pyramids, and witness the entire process of their construction.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Football Manager Simulator', 2825, 'In this new era, all national leagues have been removed and now all teams play in 4 international divisions! Have you ever thought of creating and managing a club? Create your own football club and lead it towards glory in Football Manager Simulator! Manage your squad, tactics, and finances, compete in leagues and climb to the top division, sign football stars and coach your players to make them better! However, the road to glory wont be easy... Youll need to earn the money for coaching, signing players, and academy scouting. Upgrade your stadium to win more money on home matches and get sponsors to earn crucial amounts of money!', 'Navigate through the tabs to access different functionality Squad allows you to change starting XI Transfer Market allows signing new talents League shows your league position Academy lets you scout for the next big talent Coaching improves team', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Rotate to Escape', 2826, 'Rotate to Escape is a captivating puzzle adventure where you must navigate 60 treacherous dungeon levels to find the key and break free. But danger lurks at every turn deadly traps, falling crates, and razor-sharp thorns stand in your way. The twist? You can rotate the entire dungeon to alter gravity, turning walls into walkways and pitfalls into paths. Think fast, plan your moves, and outsmart the dungeon&amp;rsquo;s tricks to claim your freedom&amp;hellip; if you dare! Can you escape, or will the maze claim another victim?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Zombie Monster Survivors', 2827, 'Zombie Monster Survivors is a role-playing game where you will become a brave survivor. Fight against terrifying zombies and monsters in an amazing world. Use your resources wisely and defeat the monsters and zombies that keep coming. Try to survive in this extreme environment. Keep moving and attack large waves of zombies. Collect coins or energy and choose your skills.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Boat Attack', 2828, 'Boat Attack is a 1-player boat racing game with a fascinating visual experience! Play as a driver of the motorboat and challenge your opponents in the boat racing championship. Control a speed boat through narrow track turns, beat all the opponents in this game with excellent visuals and sound set in the location with emerald waters and towering limestone island topped by rain forests. You can choose from two types of boats and paint the boats in the color you like.', 'WASD Arrows - drive boat Esc - return to the menu R - reload boat P - pause game', 'English'),
('The Last Light of Lyra', 2829, 'The Last Light of Lyra is a cozy, story-driven cosmic puzzle adventure set in a universe on the edge of collapse. As the last spark of hope, you guide gentle mining ships across a starmap of mysterious, fading planets&amp;mdash;transferring resources and solving intricate logic-based challenges. Beneath its dreamy visuals lies a hidden structure of clever math-inspired puzzles designed to quietly stretch your brain as you restore balance to the stars. Use addition and subtraction to solve the puzzles.', 'Mouse to drag and drop between planets', 'English'),
('Highway Racer 3D', 2830, 'Highway Racer 3D puts you in the drivers seat for the ultimate high-speed highway challenge! Race through traffic-packed roads in four thrilling game modes: One Way &amp;ndash; Navigate intense single-lane traffic and test your reflexes! Two Way &amp;ndash; Double the lanes, double the chaos! Overtake oncoming traffic and stay in control. Time Attack &amp;ndash; Beat the clock as you race to cover the longest distance before time runs out! Time Bomb &amp;ndash; A ticking time bomb adds pressure! Drive fast, avoid crashes, and defuse the danger by staying in motion.', 'WASD or Arrow Keys', 'English'),
('Santa Giftbox 2 Player', 2831, 'Be very careful, yes, the New Year has arrived, and Santa Claus and the Green Monster need to race. You need to be either the Green Monster or Santa Claus and hold the gift box in your hands. The one who holds the most gift boxes by the time the timer runs out wins. Take the gift box and avoid your friend, dont let them take it from you. To win the game, hold onto the gift box until the time runs out.', 'Use the WASD keys or the Arrow Keys to move Hold the gift box for 2 minutes to win the game When time runs out the player holding the gift box wins', 'English'),
