('Super Pop Blast', 2892, 'Get ready for a new kind of brick shooter! Clear all the blocks using a limited number balls. Plan your moves, use the score combo system, and try to get 3 stars! - 50 handcrafted levels - Unique mechanics - Colorful aesthetics - Challenging gameplay', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Arrow Away Puzzle', 2893, 'Tap Away 3d is a simple puzzle game but very relaxing to play in your spare time This game is appropriate for everyone of any age. Tap Away is brought to you by Popcore, makers of hit puzzle games with more than 250 million combined installs! Tap Away is a fun and addictive 3D puzzle game, but it&amp;rsquo;s more than just that - it&amp;rsquo;s a brain teaser that will take you to the next level!', '- Tap a cube block to move it by the arrow direction - You cannot move a cube if the front of it has another cube - Move all cubes to complete the level - Each level has a limited move number', 'English'),
('Drago Sky Quest', 2894, 'Drago Sky Quest takes you on a soaring adventure through mystical skies and floating kingdoms! Play as Drago, a brave young dragon on a mission to reclaim the lost sky crystals and restore balance to the clouds. Glide through challenging aerial paths, dodge magical traps, defeat airborne enemies, and uncover ancient secrets. With vibrant graphics, smooth flight controls, and epic boss battles, every level is a breathtaking quest above the clouds. Collect upgrades, unlock new powers, and explore enchanting sky worlds. Are you ready to spread your wings and become the hero of the heavens? Take flight in Drago Sky Quest!', 'use keyboard arrow key and mouse to play game or touch screen', 'English'),
('Monster Heroes Of Myths', 2895, 'Monster Heroes Of Myths is an action-packed adventure game where you can summon soldiers to battle against evil enemies! Its suitable for boys who love adventure! You will form your army and explore the mysterious map.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Blob Hero', 2896, 'In Blob Hero, you become a brave hero facing endless waves of enemies and monsters! This survival game offers a true rogue adventure experience. You control a blob hero, choose basic skills and upgrade to survive.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Crypto Ninja Miner', 2897, 'Crypto Ninja Miner is a fast-paced slicing game where precision and quick reflexes lead to digital riches! Swipe your finger like a true ninja to slice falling crypto coins while dodging dangerous enemy elements like bombs. The more coins you slice, the higher your score&amp;mdash;just be careful not to hit the wrong target! With smooth controls, exciting challenges, and a thrilling crypto-themed setting, Crypto Ninja Miner will test your speed and accuracy. Can you master the art of slicing and become the ultimate crypto ninja? Play now and start your mining adventure!', 'Slash and cut the fruits avoid bombs', 'English'),
('Emralds Forest Shoot', 2898, 'Emeralds Forest Shoot invites you into a magical woodland filled with sparkling treasures and hidden dangers! Grab your bow, aim carefully, and shoot through waves of mystical obstacles to collect precious emeralds scattered across the enchanted forest. Dodge tricky traps, battle mysterious creatures, and unlock powerful upgrades as you master your archery skills. With beautiful hand-crafted visuals, smooth controls, and a mix of action and strategy, every shot brings you closer to uncovering the forest&amp;rsquo;s secrets. Are you ready to become the legendary archer of the woods? Adventure awaits in the vibrant world of Emeralds Forest Shoot!', 'use mouse to play game of touch screen', 'English'),
('Geometry Dash Jump', 2899, 'Get ready for an electrifying challenge in Geometry Dash Jump Test your reflexes and timing as you jump, fly, and dash through neon-lit obstacles in a world of glowing geometry. With fast-paced action, rhythmic music, and intense gameplay, this game will push your skills to the limit!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Boosted Jetpack Hero', 2900, 'Boosted Jetpack Hero is an action-packed battlefield survival game where agility and firepower are your best allies! Equipped with a powerful jetpack, you must jump, dodge, and shoot your way through waves of bullets, cannonballs, and deadly obstacles. Stay alert and use your skills to outmaneuver every threat while fighting to stay alive! With intense gameplay, explosive action, and thrilling challenges, Boosted Jetpack Hero will test your reflexes and combat strategy. Can you survive the battlefield and emerge as the ultimate hero? Suit up, take flight, and start your mission now!', 'Save yourself', 'English'),
('Jewelry Bonney Anime One Piece', 2901, '5 Levels of a beloved anime character from One Piece, Jewelry Bonney! Try and solve tile jigsaw puzzle and unlock sexy glutton waifu Jewelry Bonney.', 'Mouse or Touch Control', 'English'),
('PolyGun: Idle TD', 2902, 'Welcome to PolyGun &amp;ndash; the ultimate idle tower defense shooter! Take command of a mighty auto-firing turret and dive into a world overrun by endless waves of geometric enemies . Each foe has its own movement pattern, and they&amp;rsquo;re not here to play nice. Upgrade, unlock, dominate Power up with cards Complete quests and challenges Earn daily rewards', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Lost Bus', 2903, 'After the last nuclear war on earth, people mutated and became zombies, some of them became unrealistic sizes, terrifying the imagination, everyone is against you, except for your devoted girl Sasha and your modernized school bus in case of X. Sometimes the military can help you, sometimes the bus modifications, and sometimes luck. Survive this HELL!!!', 'All control instructions in section control In start menu Control adapted for Desktop and Mobile devices', 'English'),
('Survive Squad', 2904, 'Welcome to Survive Squad, a hot survival game that combines Strategy and Role-Playing. In a world full of crises, you will be the commander of the squad. Lead your Heroes against endless enemies! Use your wits and strategy to survive the battlefield. Collect and lay out your weapons in your Backpack System. Merge weapons of the same type for upgrades. Flexible match equipment to create the strongest survival warrior.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Kitten Connections', 2905, 'Kitten Connections is a heartwarming puzzle adventure where adorable kittens need your help to find their perfect matches! Connect identical kittens by drawing paths across the board, solving cute and clever puzzles along the way. With each level, unlock new fluffy friends, vibrant backgrounds, and delightful surprises. Easy to play but challenging to master, Kitten Connections offers endless fun for cat lovers and puzzle fans alike. Relax with charming music, enjoy colorful visuals, and watch your kitten collection grow. Can you connect them all and create the ultimate kitten paradise? Dive into the cuteness of Kitten Connections today!', 'use mouse or touch screen for play game', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('TICTAK TOE play AI easy hard', 2906, 'Option 1: Short &amp;amp; Catchy (Tagline / Very Short Description) Classic Tic Tac Toe: Reimagined! Play PvP or challenge Easy/Hard AI. Modern Tic Tac Toe Fun! Battle friends or test your skills against the AI. Sleek Tic Tac Toe: PvP &amp;amp; AI Modes. Quick games, endless fun! Option 2: Medium Description (Standard Portal / App Store Description) Enjoy the timeless fun of Tic Tac Toe with a fresh, modern twist! Challenge your friends in local Player vs Player mode, test your skills against our casual Easy AI, or face a true test with the strategic Hard AI opponent. Featuring a sleek design with smooth animations, clear visual feedback, and a dynamic backg', 'Mouse click or tap to play and enjoy game', 'English'),
('Sprunki Piano Explorer', 2907, 'Discover Music with the Sprunki Crew. Sprunki Piano Explorer is a joyful and free to play piano game designed especially for kids who love to explore sound and creativity. It is not just a piano - it is a playground of musical discovery where little ones can tap, mix, and laugh along with a colorful cast of Sprunki characters. have fun playing!', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Tung Tung Sahur Coloring Book', 2908, 'Unleash your creativity with the Italian Tung Coloring Book, a hilarious and surreal coloring experience inspired by the viral Italian Brainrot meme phenomenon. Featuring absurd characters like Tung Tung Tung Sahur, Tralalero Tralala, and Bombardiro Crocodilo, this coloring book offers a unique blend of humor and art. Each page presents a bizarre and whimsical scene, inviting you to add your personal touch with colors. Whether youre a meme enthusiast or just looking for a fun and quirky activity, this coloring book provides endless entertainment.', 'Mouse', 'English'),
('Tung Tung  Sahur Trap Maze', 2909, 'Welcome to the exciting game Tong Tong Sahor: Maze Escape! A unique arcade awaits you, where you have to escape from the funny, but extremely dangerous character Tong Tong Sahor! Immerse yourself in a world of adventure full of intricate mazes, traps, and unexpected turns. Be quick, find the keys, and avoid meeting Tong Tong Sahor! Only the smartest and most agile will be able to find a way out! Game features: Intense chase in 3D mazes Unique character Tong Tong Sahor Exciting levels with puzzles Tense and fun atmosphere Simple and relaxing gameplay for all ages Are you ready to survive this dangerous adventure?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sweet Puzzle Adventure Quest', 2910, 'Sweet Puzzle Adventure Quest is a delightful match-3 puzzle game set in a world of delicious candies! Swap, match, and crush colorful sweets to complete exciting levels and unlock new challenges. Create powerful combos, clear obstacles, and score big to become the ultimate candy master! With hundreds of fun levels, exciting boosters, and a sugar-filled adventure, Sweet Puzzle Adventure Quest offers endless entertainment for puzzle lovers. Can you complete every level and conquer the candy kingdom? Play now and let the sweet adventure begin!', 'Match-3 and win', 'English'),
('Squareking of Easter', 2911, 'The square king needs to escape from the castle. Help the square king and leave the kingdom. During the Easter holiday, monsters attacked the castle. They surrounded it from all sides. To escape the castle, you must collect all the Easter eggs. Be careful &amp;mdash; the castle is filled with dangerous traps and sharp blades. And of course, flying and ground-running monsters are waiting for you around the castle. Reach the chest as quickly as possible and escape the castle!', 'You can move using the WASD keys Mobile controls are available Collect all the Easter eggs and reach the chest', 'English'),
('Ninja Veggie Slice', 2912, 'Step into the shoes of a ninja master in Ninja Veggie Slice! Swipe swiftly to slice flying vegetables and rack up points. Stay alert&amp;mdash;hidden bombs are scattered among the veggies and one wrong move could end your run! With smooth controls, vibrant graphics, and endless action, Ninja Veggie Slice delivers a thrilling experience for players of all ages. How long can you survive the slicing frenzy? Features: Fast-paced slicing gameplay Colorful and dynamic visuals Easy controls for mobile and desktop', 'Mobile Tap Plain veggies and Swipe with your finger across the screen Desktop Click the left button of the mouse and Drag to slice Plain veggies', 'English'),
('Gravity Zero', 2913, 'Galaxy Zero is an exciting, fast-paced arcade game where players catch falling apples using a basket, with the goal of achieving the highest score possible. The game features two thrilling modes: Speed Rounds, where apples fall at an ever-increasing pace, testing your quick reflexes and reaction time, and Survival, where you must keep catching apples without missing too many, as each mistake brings you closer to game over. Whether youre competing to beat your personal best or aiming for the top of the leaderboard, each session is a race against time and precision. Can you survive the chaos and become the ultimate apple-catching champion?', 'Drag the basket and collect the apples On computer you can also use left and rights keys', 'English'),
('Liars Bar', 2914, 'Welcome to a world of strategy, wit, and mind games in Liar&amp;rsquo;s Bar. Here, you&amp;rsquo;ll need more than just luck. Everything depends on your wits to overcome your opponents. If you like bluffing, guessing games, and a little bit of lying, then this is the game for you. Choose the Revolver Duel or Dog Duel.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Bricklayer', 2915, 'This is an interesting game of moving bricks to build a wall. Drag the bricks to build the wall. The bricks in two adjacent layers up and down should not have their joints aligned, except for the left and right sides. You will win when you have used up all the bricks.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Easter Deer', 2916, 'Easter has arrived, and you must help the reindeer! The reindeer accidentally got lost in the sky above the city. In this challenging game, help the reindeer escape the endless sky. If it falls down, you lose &amp;mdash; so don&amp;rsquo;t let it fall! Watch out for obstacles and collect all the Easter eggs. It&amp;rsquo;s Easter today, don&amp;rsquo;t miss the excitement. You must reach the finish line!', 'Use the WASD keys to move Collect all the Easter eggs The golden Easter egg is very valuable Reach the finish line safely', 'English'),
('Orbit Loop Revolution', 2917, 'Master the cosmic loop in Orbit Loop Revolution! Simple controls, deep challenge. FLIP TO SURVIVE: Tap or use keys to instantly change your orbital direction. COLLECT &amp;amp; DODGE: Grab Stars for points while avoiding relentless Hazards. POWER UP! Turn the tide with game-changing items like Shields, Slow-Mo, x2 Score, Magnets, and Ring-Clearing Blasts! LEVEL UP &amp;amp; INTENSIFY: Every 15 stars boosts the level, clears the board, and amps up the speed! FRENZY MODE: Unleash chaos every 5 levels for a high-scoring star grab! UPGRADE &amp;amp; CUSTOMIZE: Spend Star Points on permanent power-up boosts, extra lives, and even an auto-firing', 'Mouse click Spacebar Arrows or Tap to play', 'English'),
('Counter Craft Classic 2', 2918, 'Counter Craft Classic 2 is a thrilling first-person shooter that combines the best elements of Counter-Strike weapons with Minecraft-style environments. Step into blocky battlefields filled with dangerous mobs, intense firefights, and fast-paced action. Armed with iconic weapons like the AWP, AK-47, Desert Eagle, and more, your mission is simple yet challenging: eliminate enemies and find the exit on each level to progress. Each map offers unique layouts, strategic hiding spots, and waves of pixelated foes determined to stop you.', 'WASD - Move LMB - Shoot RMB - Aim Flashlight R - Reload G - Grenade H - Melee C - Crouch M - Mute Space - Jump Shift - Run 1-9 - Select Weapon', 'English'),
('Buckshot Roulette', 2919, 'Do you dare to bet your life on an exciting roulette wheel showdown? Buckshot Roulette is a gun simulator that combines strategy, shooting and survival. Instead of a pistol, a powerful shotgun was used. Every pull of the trigger is a choice of fate. The winner lives, the loser dies. You will begin a Turn-Based shooting roulette game. Each round will have a fixed number of bullets and blanks.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Number Order', 2920, 'Number Order is a fun and brain-boosting puzzle game that challenges your logic and speed! Arrange numbers in the correct sequence by sliding, tapping, or swapping tiles across different grids and difficulty levels. It starts easy but quickly tests your sharpness with increasingly tricky patterns and time limits. Perfect for players of all ages, Number Order is a simple yet addictive way to sharpen your mind, improve focus, and have fun. Unlock new themes, beat your high scores, and master the art of perfect sequencing. Get ready to think fast and stay sharp with the exciting world of Number Order!', 'use mouse or touch screen for play game', 'English'),
('Food Merge', 2921, 'Food Merge is a game where you combine different foods to create delicious dishes and serve them to hungry customers. Merge ingredients quickly and strategically to before the time runs out! Each level brings new challenges, faster orders, and more complex combos. Can you keep up and become the ultimate food master?', 'Everything is controller by mouse or touch', 'English'),
('Christmas Cooking Chef', 2922, 'Hi, all you awesome girls out there who love to cook! Christmas is just around the corner and it&amp;rsquo;s time to play the ultimate Christmas cooking chef in this super fun cooking simulator! In Christmas Cooking Chef you&amp;rsquo;ll enter a magical virtual kitchen full of festive cheer. This super casual game is perfect for anyone to start cooking festive meals right away.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Grand Crime City', 2923, 'Step into the gritty streets of Grand Crime City, where danger lurks around every corner and only the toughest survive. In this action-packed shooter game, youll take on the role of a fearless vigilante completing intense missions to bring order&amp;mdash;or chaos&amp;mdash;to the city. With 20 thrilling missions, each more challenging than the last, youll be chasing down enemies, taking out rival gangs, and fighting to survive in an urban warzone. Explore the open city, accept tasks, and prove your dominance in the crime underworld.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Deep Sea Catch Fun', 2924, 'Deep Sea Catch Fun is an exciting fish-catching adventure where a clever cat dives into the ocean for the ultimate catch! Drop the anchor, aim carefully, and hook a fish from the deep waters. But the challenge doesn&amp;rsquo;t end there&amp;mdash;once the fish leaps out of the water, you must tap it again to secure your catch! With fun mechanics, adorable animations, and fast-paced gameplay, Deep Sea Catch Fun is a thrilling test of timing and reflexes. Can you help the cat reel in the biggest catch and master the sea? Play now and start your fishing adventure!', 'Catch the fishes', 'English'),
('Word it UP', 2925, 'Word it UP challenges players to drag letters and create words to complete each level. With multiple levels awaiting, the game tests vocabulary and strategic skills. Can you conquer the increasingly difficult puzzles to become the ultimate word master? Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.bestcrazygames.com/''&gt;https://www.bestcrazygames.com/&lt;/a&gt;', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Red Escape', 2926, 'Red Escape is a captivating adventure puzzle game that puts your wits and problem-solving skills to the test! Trapped in a series of three rooms, your goal is to use logic, gather tools, uncover hidden clues, and solve intricate puzzles to make your escape. Do you have the skills to solve every puzzle and escape all three rooms?', 'Use the left mouse button to interact with in-game UI', 'English'),
('Sprunki Idle Clicker', 2927, 'Sprunki Idle Clicker : A Fun and Addictive Clicker Adventure With Sprunkies. The main idea of Sprunki Idle Clicker is simple : click as fast as you can to collect points and unlock new Sprunkies. Each tap adds to your progress, pushing you closer to new rewards and even more adorable characters. The more you click, the more you grow. It is a game of pure satisfaction as you watch numbers go up and new creatures join your collection.', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Italian Brainrot Tung Sahur Snake.io', 2928, 'Italian Brainrot Tung Sahur Snake.io is a hilarious and chaotic twist on the classic slither.io gameplay, infused with the energy of viral Italian Brainrot memes! Dive into an arena where your snake isn&amp;rsquo;t just a plain old serpent &amp;mdash; it&amp;rsquo;s a wriggling parade of internet insanity, with famous meme characters like Tung Tung Sahur, Brr Brr Patapim, Ballerina Cappucina, and Ralalero trALALA leading the charge as the snake&amp;rsquo;s animated, expressive head! In this wildly entertaining multiplayer experience, you start small &amp;mdash; just a tiny meme slithering around &amp;mdash; but your goal is to grow bigger, longer, and more ridiculous by eating glowing orbs scattered', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Stickman Skate City', 2929, 'Stickman Skate City is an exciting skateboarding action game where players control a nimble stickman character to perform amazing skateboard tricks in a vast urban environment. In this open world, players can freely explore every corner of the city, challenge various obstacles, and complete dazzling 360-degree spins and other high-difficulty stunts.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Perfect Cake Maker', 2930, 'Get ready to make some seriously delicious cakes in Perfect Cake Maker! It&amp;rsquo;s a delightful casual simulation game. When you start, you&amp;rsquo;ll see a fully stocked kitchen and delicious guests waiting. First, choose the cake base based on your guests&amp;rsquo; needs. Then comes the fun part &amp;ndash; mixing the ingredients!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Tung Tung Tung Sahur Jigsaw Puzzle', 2931, 'Step into the world of Tung Tung Tung Sahur with this fun and engaging jigsaw puzzle game! Challenge your mind and enjoy the thrill of solving puzzles with amazing images from the Tung Tung Tung Sahur series. Whether you&amp;rsquo;re a puzzle enthusiast or a Tung Tung Tung Sahur fan, this game offers endless hours of entertainment as you piece together captivating visuals.', 'Touch Pad or Mouse click Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Rainbow Ice Cream Maker', 2932, 'Hey, all you girls with a sweet tooth! Get ready to enter a world of sweet joy! Rainbow Ice Cream Maker is the best casual cooking simulator out there! In this game, you&amp;rsquo;re an ice cream chef in a magical, colorful kitchen. The goal? To make the most mouth-watering, rainbow-colored ice cream! First, you pick the base flavor of your ice cream. It can be creamy vanilla, tangy chocolate, or tart strawberry.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Resident Evil: Purge Operation', 2933, 'At the start of each level, players must quickly locate powerful weapons like the shotgun and sniper rifle, crucial for fending off hordes of zombies. Once the eerie alarm sounds, grotesque, ferocious undead flood the area. A single mistake can lead to being swarmed, so precise marksmanship, agile movement, and calm judgment are essential for survival.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Crescent Solitaire', 2934, 'Crescent Solitaire is a captivating card game where the objective is to move all cards from the outer tableau piles to the eight foundation piles in the center. Players must stack the aces up to the kings in suit while also placing kings down to aces in suit. Cards can be moved within the tableaus as long as they are of the same suit and the card being placed is directly higher or lower in value than the card beneath it. With its unique crescent layout and strategic gameplay, Crescent Solitaire offers a delightful challenge for fans of traditional solitaire!', 'Mouse click', 'English'),
('Stick Warrior', 2935, 'Stick Warrior is an intense side-scrolling action game featuring stick figure warriors in an epic battle for survival. Players take on the role of a legendary stick warrior who must fight through hordes of enemies, master various combat techniques, and overcome challenging obstacles to restore peace to the realm.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Fish Pot', 2936, 'Fish Pot is a delightful and addictive game where your goal is to catch and collect colorful fish into the perfect pot! Tap, aim, and guide the fish through tricky paths, avoiding obstacles and making sure each fish lands safely. With vibrant underwater environments, relaxing music, and simple one-touch controls, Fish Pot offers a calming yet challenging experience for players of all ages. Unlock new types of fish, upgrade your pots, and discover beautiful aquatic worlds as you progress. Ready to test your skills and fill your pot with the ocean&amp;rsquo;s finest? Dive into the fun of Fish Pot today!', 'use mouse click or touch screen to play game', 'English'),
('Go Chicken Go', 2937, 'Guide your flock from the left side to safety! Each chicken needs your help to navigate treacherous multi-lane highways filled with speeding traffic and a wide, dangerous river. Dodge cars, trucks, and hop across logs and lily pads. Timing is everything! Can you get every chicken across?', 'Keyboard and On screen controls', 'English'),
('Dog and Cat Sweet', 2938, 'Are you ready for the adventure of Dog and Cat? A super exhausting journey awaits you. There are obstacles everywhere, and you must be very careful. The cat and dog must be like siblings. They need to work together as a team; otherwise, they wont reach the doghouse at the finish line. They must collect all the food they find on the way because the cat and dog must not go hungry. Gather all the food you find, watch out for obstacles, cross the bridge and the iron gate, and reach the doghouse.', 'Move using the WASD and Arrow Keys Only the dog can open the bridge and the iron gate Playable on both mobile and PC Collect all the cat and dog food and reach the doghouse', 'English'),
('Maze Escape Toilet Rush', 2939, 'Whats the most urgent situation you can imagine? Of course, it is the last second of finding a toilet. In Maze Escape: Toilet Rush, youll have a nervous and hilarious maze escape. Each level is a brand-new maze. You need to find the best route to the toilet quickly. Use your logic and intelligence to reach your destination successfully.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Click And Colors Dinosaurs', 2940, 'Description: Get ready for a colorful prehistoric adventure! In Click and Color Dinosaur, kids can bring adorable dinosaurs to life by simply clicking on different parts of the picture to color them. Choose from a vibrant palette and enjoy an easy, fun, and educational experience. Perfect for young artists and dinosaur lovers! Features: Easy one-click coloring gameplay Cute dinosaurs and prehistoric scenes Bright and colorful graphics Kid-friendly interface Great for creativity and hand-eye coordination How to Play: Click on the outlined parts of the image to fill them with colors. Complete the whole picture and have fun!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Kitchen King Rush', 2941, 'Kitchen King Rush is a fast-paced restaurant game where hungry customers arrive, and it&amp;rsquo;s up to you to serve them delicious meals on time! Cook, plate, and deliver a variety of mouthwatering dishes while managing the kitchen chaos. Keep your customers happy, earn big tips, and upgrade your restaurant to become the ultimate Kitchen King! With vibrant graphics, exciting challenges, and addictive gameplay, this culinary adventure will test your speed and strategy. Available in English and Espa&amp;ntilde;ol, dive into the fun and prove your skills as the best chef in town! &amp;zwj; &amp;iexcl;Juega ahora y convi&amp;eacute;rtete en el rey de la cocina!', 'Serve food ASAP', 'English'),
('Mystery Campus Spotter', 2942, 'Mystery Campus Spotter is a thrilling find-the-difference game set in a vibrant college campus! Sharpen your observation skills as you compare two nearly identical images and uncover hidden differences before time runs out. From bustling classrooms to lively dorms and secret study spots, every scene is packed with intriguing details waiting to be discovered! With multiple difficulty levels, stunning visuals, and engaging gameplay, Mystery Campus Spotter offers a fun and challenging experience for all ages. Can you spot all the differences and unravel the campus mysteries? Play now and put your detective skills to the test! &amp;zwj;', 'Click and match', 'English'),
('Ring Master Legends', 2943, 'Ring Master Legends is an action-packed boxing game that tests your speed, reflexes, and precision! Step into the ring and punch your way to victory by matching your gloves to the falling balls&amp;mdash;use the Red glove for red balls and the Blue glove for blue balls. The more accurate your hits, the higher your score! With fast-paced gameplay, dynamic animations, and increasing difficulty, Ring Master Legends will keep you on your toes as you strive for the ultimate high score. Do you have what it takes to become a true legend of the ring? Step in, gear up, and start punching!', 'Click and break the balls', 'English'),
('Pool Legends Pro Masters', 2944, 'Pool Legends Pro Master is a fast-paced billiards game where precision and speed are the keys to victory! Aim, shoot, and sink the balls as quickly as possible to rack up high scores and dominate the table. The faster you clear the table, the better your rank! With realistic physics, smooth controls, and exciting challenges, Pool Legends Pro Master offers an immersive pool experience for casual players and pros alike. Do you have what it takes to become the ultimate pool legend? Grab your cue and start playing now!', 'Play Pool', 'English'),
('Children Happy Farm DuDu', 2945, 'Hey there, little farmers in the making! Welcome to Children Happy Farm DuDu! This is an amazing casual simulator designed just for your kids. In this fun-filled farm world, youll be the boss of your farm. The farm is full of cute animals like fluffy sheep, clucking chickens, and friendly cows. Your job is to take good care of them. Feed the animals, clean their shelters, and make sure they are happy.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('TB Avataria Life Girl', 2946, 'Hey, how about helping me decorate my house? You need to decorate my home beautifully, buy me nice clothes, and feed me. Lets get started &amp;mdash; right now, I have an empty house, and we need to furnish it together. Lets make it look organized and cozy! Before I get too hungry, you must take me to the caf&amp;eacute; to eat, or I might lose my life from hunger! We also need to earn money. To make money, reach the computer and use the money-making app. You can either buy things or continue earning more money!', 'Use the WASD keys to move Playable on both mobile and PC 4 different hairstyles and 4 different outfits are waiting for you 2 different ways to earn money', 'English'),
('Smoke man runner 2d', 2947, 'Smoke Man Runner 2D is an action-packed endless runner game where every jump counts. With clean visuals, catchy music, and simple controls, its a fun and addictive game for players of all ages.', 'TOUCH CONTROLLER', 'English'),
('Bridge Race   Test of Precision', 2948, 'Bridge Race is an exciting online game that challenges your focus, timing, and quick reflexes. The main goal is to guide your bridge safely across different platforms by passing it through various shaped gaps &amp;mdash; without crashing! As the bridge moves forward, players must quickly adjust its height or width to match the upcoming obstacles. Each level becomes more challenging, with faster speeds and trickier shapes that test your reaction time and hand-eye coordination. One wrong move, and your bridge will crash! Perfect for players who enjoy fast-paced, skill-based games,', 'Bridge Race combines simple controls with addictive gameplay making it easy to pick up but hard to master Can you keep your bridge intact and race to the finish', 'English'),
('Planetary Plunge', 2949, 'Planetary Plunge hurls you into a thrilling cosmic free-fall across the galaxy! Navigate your way through asteroid fields, dodge alien obstacles, and dive deeper into mysterious planets as you race for survival. With fast-paced action, stunning space environments, and easy one-touch controls, every plunge is a heart-racing adventure. Collect cosmic power-ups, unlock new astronaut suits, and challenge yourself with increasingly difficult worlds. Will you master the art of the perfect fall and become the ultimate space explorer? Prepare for a breathtaking descent and discover the unknown in the thrilling journey of Planetary Plunge!', 'use arroww key on keyboard for play game darr Down arrow to light Brown uarr Upper arrow Silver larr Left arrow yellow brown rarr Right arrow dark brown', 'English'),
('Tralalero Tralala Red Light Squid Game', 2950, 'Tralalero Tralala: Red Light Squid Game is a thrilling, hilarious twist on the classic Red Light Green Light challenge &amp;mdash; and it&amp;rsquo;s more intense, more unpredictable, and packed with crazy surprises! Step into the sneakers of Talalelo, the legendary shark hero&amp;rsquo;s mischievous twin, as he takes on the deadliest version of the Squid Game yet. But this time, it&amp;rsquo;s not an ordinary doll calling the shots &amp;mdash; it&amp;rsquo;s Ballerina Cappucina, a graceful yet terrifying ballerina with a cappuccino cup for a head, whose elegant dance hides ruthless precision! Your mission is clear: survive the Red Light Green Light stage by moving swiftly during the green phase and', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Geometry Dash BeatBox', 2951, 'Jump and fly your way through danger in this rhythm-based action platformer! Prepare for a near-impossible challenge in the world of Geometry Dash. Push your skills to the limit as you jump, fly and flip your way through dangerous passages and spiky obstacles. Simple one-touch game play with lots of levels that will keep you entertained for hours! Game Features &amp;bull; Rhythm-based Action Platforming! &amp;bull; Lots of levels with unique soundtracks! &amp;bull; Build and share your levels using the level editor! &amp;bull; Unlock new icons and colours to customise your character! &amp;bull; Fly rockets, flip gravity and much more! &amp;bull; Use practice mode to sharpen your skills!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Swipe Runner Quest', 2952, 'Swipe Runner Quest is an exciting coin-collection adventure where speed and precision are your best allies! Swipe to move, dodge obstacles, and collect every coin on your path as you race toward the final gate. Stay focused&amp;mdash;one wrong move could cost you victory! With smooth controls, challenging levels, and thrilling gameplay, Swipe Runner Quest will test your reflexes and strategy. Can you collect all the coins and reach the finish line unscathed? Play now and prove your skills in this ultimate running quest! &amp;zwj;', 'Use arrow keys to move', 'English'),
('Slippery Descent By Car', 2953, 'Pass obstacles on cars from the cube game! A hardcore game that takes you into an exciting world of gambling challenges. You have to conquer dangerous descents on various cars, overcoming the most difficult obstacles on the way to victory. Each level is unique, full of surprises and challenges!', 'The machines are controlled by the standard WASD keys or the arrows on the keyboard You can control the car in the air bull Space mdash handbrake bull C mdash change the camera view bull R mdash level reset bull H mdash main menu', 'English'),
('Angry Battle Birds Mania', 2954, 'Angry Battle Bird Mania is an action-packed bird-flinging adventure where precision and strategy lead to victory! Load your fiercest birds into the catapult, take aim, and launch them to smash through enemy structures. The fewer shots you use to destroy all obstacles, the higher your score! With exciting physics-based gameplay, powerful bird abilities, and challenging levels, Angry Battle Bird Mania will keep you hooked for hours. Can you master the perfect shot and bring down every enemy structure? Play now and unleash the ultimate bird battle!', 'Click and aim Use slingshot', 'English'),
('Healthy Hero', 2955, 'Healthy Hero is an exciting and educational action game where you play as a brave hero fighting off junk food monsters! Help your character stay healthy by collecting fruits and vegetables while avoiding sugary treats. Quick reflexes and smart moves will help you win each challenge. With colorful graphics, fast-paced gameplay, and an important message about healthy living, Healthy Hero is perfect for players of all ages.', 'Desktop Click the left Button of the mouse to jump player to avoid gap and junk food One Click for one jump and double click for double jump Mobile Tap the screen to jump player to avoid gaps and junk food One tap for one jump and double tap for dou', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Target master 2D', 2956, 'throws you into a fast-paced arcade ride where every shot counts. Aim your glowing ball, calculate perfect arcs, and blast through tricky obstacles in a world full of vibrant lights and smooth momentum. It&amp;rsquo;s not just about jumping &amp;mdash; it&amp;rsquo;s about timing, precision, and style. Bounce, shoot, and slide through insane 3D levels that keep getting harder the further you go. One mistake, and it&amp;rsquo;s game over. But nailing that perfect jump? So satisfying. Whether youre here to chill or chase high scores, Glow Jump 3D is your next addictive shooting ball challenge. Can you master the perfect jump?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('StickBoys Hook', 2957, 'Swing with Stickboys and jump your way to the finish line. Stickboys needs your help. Assist him and reach the goal! Jump from launch ramps and shoot webs to get to the end. You must complete every level. Be careful &amp;mdash; if you fall from the sky, you lose the game.', 'Click or tap to rope 20 different challenging levels Mobile controls available', 'English'),
('Tung Tung Sahur Hidden Bedug', 2958, 'Get ready to dive into a festive hidden object adventure with a twist! In Tung Tung Sahur: Hidden Bedug, your mission is simple&amp;mdash;but don&amp;rsquo;t be fooled, its not as easy as it sounds! Objective: Find all 10 hidden bedug (traditional Indonesian drums) cleverly camouflaged in each level. They&amp;rsquo;re sneakily tucked away between lively &amp;ldquo;Tung Tung&amp;rdquo; pictures, echoing the spirit of sahur traditions during Ramadan. Game Highlights: Colorful, cheerful sahur-themed artwork Increasing difficulty with every level A race against time (depending on how you play!) Perfect for kids and families looking for a Ramadan-themed game night', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Carnival Shooter', 2959, 'Carnival Shooter brings the fun of the fair to your fingertips! Step right up and test your aim in this vibrant, fast-paced shooting gallery. Blast balloons, knock down cans, hit moving targets, and score big to win exciting prizes. With colorful carnival-themed visuals, satisfying sound effects, and a variety of quirky challenges, every level feels like a trip to the amusement park. Unlock new levels, power-ups, and custom blasters as you climb the high score board. Whether youre a sharpshooter or just in for some fun, Carnival Shooter is your ticket to non-stop arcade excitement!', 'Use Mouse to play game', 'English'),
('Capybara Go!', 2960, 'Enter the wonderful world of Capybara. In Capybara Go, begin a strategic adventure. Youll be forming and commanding your own little Capybara army. Defeat your opponents and conquer everything through strategy and combat. Lay out your Capybaras to take advantage of each ones strengths and use strategy to defeat powerful enemies.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Weight Gain Diet Cooking Recipe', 2961, 'Get ready for a mouth-watering adventure with Weight Gain Diet - Cooking Recipes! This is not your average cooking game, but a delightful simulator that combines the fun of cooking with the charm of relaxing. In this game, food takes center stage. You will see a wide variety of ingredients, from fresh produce to gourmet meals. The recipes are fun and varied, guiding you step by step to make delicious dishes.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Power Slap', 2962, 'Power Slap is an exciting slap battle game where timing, precision, and reflexes are the key to victory! Engage in fast-paced slap duels, test your skills, and out-slap your opponents to dominate the leaderboards. With simple one-tap controls, smooth animations, and addictive arcade-style gameplay, every match is a thrilling challenge. Unlock power-ups, upgrades, and special abilities to gain an edge in battle. Enjoy quick, casual fun anytime, whether youre playing solo or competing with friends. Do you have what it takes to become the ultimate slap master? Play now and prove your skills!', 'Just click tap on screen', 'English'),
('Node Fusion Frenzy', 2963, 'Node Fusion Frenzy is a high-energy puzzle and strategy game that will keep your brain buzzing! Dive into a futuristic grid where your goal is to merge glowing nodes, spark chain reactions, and clear the board with satisfying combos. How to play: Drag and combine matching nodes to create higher-level fusions. Trigger epic chain reactions and rack up massive scores. Watch out for limited moves&amp;mdash;every decision counts! With vibrant visuals, smooth controls, and brain-teasing mechanics, Node Fusion Frenzy is perfect for fans of merge games, logic puzzles, and fast-paced thinking.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Retro Pong', 2964, 'Step into gaming history with Retro Pong, a digital revival of the classic arcade experience! This simple yet legendary game pits two paddles against each other in a fast-paced volley of bouncing pixels. Score by sending the ball past your opponent&amp;mdash;first to 5 wins! Perfect for quick breaks or friendly showdowns, this old-school gem proves that sometimes, the simplest games are the most addictive. Are you quick enough to claim victory?', 'Control is available for one or two players using the keyboard', 'English'),
('Mysterious Doors', 2965, 'Explore the mysterious kingdom! Navigate levels filled with traps, puzzles, and surprises. Skill and strategy! Master the controls and discover hidden secrets as you advance through the kingdom. Are you up for the challenge? Test your speed and wits to overcome obstacles and solve puzzles!', 'Mobile Controls Use the on-screen buttons to move and jump PC Controls Use the WASD or arrow keys to move and the space bar to jump', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Tung Tung Sahur GTA Miami', 2966, 'Tung Tung Sahur: GTA Miami drops you into the chaotic, neon-soaked streets of Miami during the holy month of Ramadan. As the city sleeps, you ride through the night on a wild, action-packed mission to wake up the neighborhoods for sahur &amp;mdash; the pre-dawn meal. Armed with your trusty tung tung (drum), a motorbike that somehow defies physics, and a playlist of hyped-up beats, your job is to finish your mission &amp;mdash; and maybe cause a little mayhem along the way. But watch out: rival sahur crews, annoyed citizens, and the Miami PD aren&amp;rsquo;t going to make it easy.', 'WASD - move F - fly', 'English'),
('Sprunki Satellite Catcher', 2967, 'Sprunki Satellite Catcher: Soar Through Space And Catch Satellites. Fun and free to play online game designed especially for kids who enjoy simple and exciting space-themed adventures. This colorful game puts players in control of a cheerful Sprunki character as it floats through outer space collecting satellites. Your goal is to grab as many satellites as you can without touching the top or bottom edges of the screen. With easy to learn controls and endless replay value, this game is perfect for casual gamers and young players looking for a playful arcade experience.', 'Arrow keys or WAD to play', 'English'),
('Starry Style Dorama of Dream', 2968, 'Welcome to an exciting journey into the world of Korean doramas heroes! Here you can become a stylist for two aspiring young film actors: a young actress whose heart beats to the rhythm of romantic stories, and a charismatic actor whose smile can melt even the coldest hearts. You will be able to choose from a variety of outfits, accessories and hairstyles, creating unique images that emphasize the individuality of your characters. Diving into the world of fashion and style, you will not only help young actors shine on the screen, but also reveal your creative abilities in creating images from your favorite doramas.', 'Depending on the gaming device either a click of a computer mouse or a simple touch on touchscreens is used to control it', 'English'),
('Helicopter Battle Steve 2 Player', 2969, 'Get on the helicopter and choose either the blue or red player. Destroy your friend&amp;rsquo;s helicopter to win the game.Winning is simple: just don&amp;rsquo;t let your helicopter crash! Jump and shoot to defeat your opponent. To beat the red or blue player, you must play your best. The player whose helicopter explodes the most will lose the game.', 'To use the red helicopter press the W key To use the blue helicopter press the Up Arrow Key The first to reach 10 points wins', 'English'),
('Crack eggs', 2970, 'Crack the Egg to get the chick out!! in this awesome Clicker game The egg takes 40 crackings until its cracked.Thanks for click! lol~', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Cat From Hell Cat Simulator', 2971, 'Become the troublemaking cat in Cat From Hell - Cat Simulator. Run wild inside Granny&amp;rsquo;s house, knocking things over and making a mess, such as breaking plates, throwing balls, smashing fish tanks, etc. Escape before she catches you. Explore, prank, and cause chaos in this hilarious and mischievous cat simulator. Every corner hides a secret that can be destroyed, and discover new challenges.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Mobile Legends Slime 3v3', 2972, 'Mobile Legends Slime 3v3 will bring you into a fun arena of exciting battles! In this 3v3 PvP game, you can unblock many slime characters. Enter a variety of colorful battle scenes. Each character has unique skills and fighting styles, ensuring you find the best gameplay.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('2D Obby Rainbow Parkour', 2973, 'In the Rainbow Obby, you must complete the course without falling down. The Rainbow Obby is difficult, and sometimes, even if you play your best, you may not reach the end. Strive to reach the end of the course and complete it. Overcome the toughest parts of the course and collect all the coins.', 'Use the WASD keys to move Press the W key to jump and double jump Collect all the coins and reach the end of the level safely', 'English'),
('Radiation Zone', 2974, 'It is FPS shooter with zombies and military. Your mission is to clear area from all terrorists on the restricted radiation zone. You can find and use many kind of weapons and amo on the area. Available for You inventory, where you can collect a loot for surving. For make a tent, you need to collect a four clothes and four branches. Also You need to find a water and food for a life. Good luck for complex mission!', 'WASD - Movement Ctrl - Crouch LShift - Sprint Q E - Lean left right F - PickUp Or Inspect Weapon Box 1 2 3 - Switch Weapons G - Grenade LMB - Fire RMB - Aim Tab - Inventory Double click on item - to use Double right click -drop', 'English'),
('Chinese Cuisine Chef', 2975, 'Are you ready to become a top Chinese Cuisine Chef? Dive into this idle simulation game where you&amp;rsquo;ll master the art of Chinese cooking and run your bustling restaurant! Build your bun shop first, build tables, reception, kitchen, etc. Gradually expand your shop, unlock takeout, hire more staff, etc.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Merge fruits: Fold the Watermelon!', 2976, 'This is a game where you have to connect fruits! Compete with friends and colleagues! In the game you have a game zone where fruits fall and connect if they are the same! Connect as many fruits as possible to get a watermelon, collect points! Be the first on the leaderboard! Play and relax!', '1 At first it will be easy to connect fruits but over time there will be more and more As soon as you connect a watermelon it will disappear and give you the most points', 'English'),
('Color Fan Color By Number', 2977, 'Welcome to the colorful world of Color Fan - Color By Number! This game brings endless color fun,suitable for anyone who loves drawing and puzzles! With simple digital color matching, you can turn white paper into a gorgeous work of art!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Basketball School', 2978, 'Basketball School is the basketball arcade game in which you must try to score baskets in all the different game modes available. You can play either arcade, time attack, and distance mode. Arcade mode gives you 10 balls to use; you must continue to score baskets although it becomes harder each time you score. Time attack mode requires you to score as many baskets within the time limit as possible; you have unlimited balls but limited time. Distance mode allows you to increase the distance of your shot each time that you score.', 'Drag left mouse button to aim release to shoot', 'English'),
('Gravity Climb Girl', 2979, 'Gravity Climb Girl is a thrilling vertical adventure where gravity is your greatest challenge! Join a fearless girl on her mission to defy the laws of physics as she scales walls, leaps between platforms, and avoids deadly traps in a futuristic world. Switch gravity, dodge obstacles, and time your moves perfectly to survive intense climbing levels. With stylish graphics, smooth controls, and fast-paced gameplay, every climb is a heart-pounding test of skill and reflex. Unlock new outfits, conquer tricky levels, and become a gravity-defying legend. Are you ready to rise above? Let the Gravity Climb Girl journey begin!', 'Mouse click to play', 'English'),
('Candy Chain Master', 2980, 'Welcome to Candy Chain Master! The board has blue tiles with candies on them. Start by selecting a candy and move across nearby tiles with the same candy to make a chain of three or more. Each tile must turn golden by matching at least one candy on it. Think carefully and move fast to turn all tiles golden before time runs out.', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game', 'English'),
('dogecoin clicker', 2981, 'Click the dogecoin and do upgrades like autoclicker and dogecoins per click, and you have achievements like getting 100 dogecoins, so what are you waiting for? Start clicking! :D', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Bucket Crusher ASMR', 2982, 'Love relaxing ASMR destruction games? In Bucket Crusher ASMR, you control a powerful crusher arm to demolish pixel walls and structures. Crush them to pieces to complete the progress and pass the level. Control the bucket arm to pulverize every brick and every pixel with precision. Upgrade its length, size and power. Upgrade your machine, extend your reach, and experience the most satisfying crushing simulation ever.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Tung Tung Sahur Midnight Terror', 2983, 'In a small, forgotten town where time seems to stand still, every night of Ramadan echoes with an eerie sound... &amp;ldquo;Tung Tung Sahur!&amp;rdquo; But this is no ordinary wake-up call. Welcome to Tung Tung Sahur: Midnight Terror &amp;mdash; a bizarre horror-comedy survival game where instant noodles may be your only ticket to freedom. You play as an unsuspecting villager trapped inside an abandoned, crumbling house &amp;mdash; one that&amp;rsquo;s home to mysterious forces. Your mission? Collect 10 packs of instant noodles scattered throughout the haunted property before the break of dawn. Only then can you unlock the exit and make your escape. But beware... youre not alone. Roaming', 'WASD - move Shift - run space - grab item', 'English'),
('Bottle Solitaire', 2984, 'Game objective: Clear as many bottles as possible. It would be the best if there is only one bottle left in the end and it is located at the very center. Click to select the bottle you want to move. The positions where it can jump to will be automatically shown. Just click on the target position.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Animal Sort   Cute Game Puzzle', 2985, 'Are you a pet person? Do you wanna run a farm that is full of cute animals? Try Animal Sort, not only be an owner but also be in charge of keeping them in line - the game you should not look away. This is not just a regular puzzle game, but its also a fantastic one with a lot of mini games included. Moreover, we have an additional mode of building the pet city that you definitely wont be able to miss. Lets give it a try!', 'Using mouse to move the animal', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Weird Toilet Flush!', 2986, 'Defend the city gate from waves of invading Weird Toilets! Click the flush button to eliminate enemies before they breach the entrance. Face 20 intense levels, including powerful boss battles. Earn coins to upgrade defenses, buy weapons, and restore health. With increasing difficulty, fast-paced action, and strategic upgrades, can you stop the final boss and save the city?', 'Click Tap the flush button to stop Weird Toilets Upgrade defenses and survive all waves to win', 'English'),
('Sprunki Easter Coloring', 2987, 'Sprunki Easter Coloring is an exciting and colorful online game designed especially for kids who love to explore their imagination. This delightful digital coloring book lets young artists express themselves through a fun and festive Easter theme. With charming Sprunki characters and spring-inspired backgrounds, children can dive into a world of creativity that is both relaxing and full of color. And the best part&amp;mdash;it is completely free to play online.', 'Mouse to play', 'English'),
('Granny GTA Vegas', 2988, 'Granny GTA Vegas drops the infamous horror legend into the heart of sin city! Armed and unhinged, Granny escapes her haunted house and brings chaos to the neon streets of Las Vegas. With red-hooded masked enemies hot on her trail, she must shoot her way through crime-ridden alleys, casino districts, and the Vegas Strip. Run, shoot, and wreak havoc in this action-packed open-world mayhem, blending GTA-style gameplay with classic action vibes. Can you survive the heat and conquer the city, or will Granny become a permanent ghost of Vegas?', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Worms Lines', 2989, 'In Worms Lines, youll embark on a fun and challenging puzzle adventure across 80 exciting levels. Your task is to gather all the colored dots and cover every tile with vibrant paint, but be cautious&amp;mdash;one wrong move could lead to failure. As you navigate the maze-like environment, youll need to think strategically to reach your goal. Use holes to access new areas, but always plan your steps carefully to avoid getting stuck. Can you conquer every level and complete your painting mission?', 'Use Mouse for desktop and Touch Controls for mobile device', 'English'),
('Kitkat   Fun Puzzle', 2990, 'Enter the world of Kitkat Puzzle, a captivating and intricate pin puzzle game where your strategic thinking and creativity are put to the test. The mission is straightforward - unlock kitkat holes to make these chocolate bars fall in the correct sequence. Sounds simple, yet with unlimited levels of varying complexity, it promises an intriguing brain-teasing journey.', 'Mouse click to play', 'English'),
('Mystic Flower Match', 2991, 'Mystic Flower Match is a magical match-3 puzzle game where nature and enchantment bloom together! Dive into a vibrant world of mystical gardens filled with glowing flowers, ancient runes, and charming creatures. Match three or more blossoms to clear levels, unlock powerful boosts, and uncover hidden secrets in each stage. With relaxing music, beautifully crafted visuals, and hundreds of brain-teasing levels, this game offers a soothing yet engaging escape. Whether youre chasing high scores or simply unwinding, Mystic Flower Match is your perfect floral fantasy. Step into the garden of wonders and let the magic of matching begin!', 'use mouse to play the game', 'English'),
('Green Portal', 2992, 'Welcome to the ultimate online jigsaw puzzle experience designed to challenge and entertain players of all ages and skill levels. Categories Nature Wonders - breathtaking landscapes and natural phenomena Wildlife Gallery - stunning animal portraits Floral Collection - beautiful flowers and botanical art How to Play Select your preferred puzzle category and difficulty level. Drag and Drop pieces to their correct positions Complete the puzzle and unlock new levels', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Balls Vs Lasers', 2993, 'Begin a wonderful arcade challenge. In Balls Vs Lasers, your skill and reaction speed will be limited. Control two balls and avoid incoming lasers. Flexible avoiding and challenging your extreme operation. Control the movement of the two balls and avoid the oncoming laser attacks! Place balls of the same color against the corresponding laser.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Sprunki Happy Easter 2Player', 2994, 'The Sprunki brothers are competing against each other this Easter. The player who collects the most Easter eggs wins the game. Show your sibling or friend that youre the better player. Collect the eggs as fast as you can and bring them to the chest. Whoever delivers the most eggs to the chest wins the game.', 'Use the WASD and Arrow keys to move The player who collects 20 eggs wins Take the egg from the balloon and bring it to the chest Mobile touch control available', 'English'),
('Horror Playtime Room Escape', 2995, 'Challenge your brain to break through the fog of horror. In Horror Playtime - Room Escape you will enter a mysterious story. You spend your birthday with Ye Chen on the roof of a building. The strange woman suddenly appeared and trapped you in a horrible room. Enter many rooms full of puzzles and horror! Use your brain to solve hidden things and uncover the truth of horror stories. Every detail in the room is full of mystery.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Idle Zombie Wave', 2996, 'Zombies are invading, and the world is on the brink of collapse! In this apocalyptic survival clash, you will command a team of survivors as a smart and decisive leader. The undead horde is relentless, and only you can lead the survivors in this tower defense (TD) battle to defend your home from wave after wave of the undead.', 'Tap or Click', 'English'),
('Counter Terror 3d', 2997, 'Dive into the action-packed world of Counter Terror, a game that blends the excitement of CS with high-speed car battles. With over 10 types of weapons, 8 dynamic maps, and 4 customizable cars, the adrenaline never stops! Choose your side in thrilling game modes like DeathMatch and Team DeathMatch, and climb the military ranks from a common soldier to the prestigious General, unlocking more powerful weapons with each promotion. Explore the urban chaos in maps like Big City and GTA SA, where you can spawn cars from the garage, turning the battlefield into a vehicular warzone.', 'Tab - Open Menu P - Full Screen E Q - Change Weapon 1 2 3 Mouse Wheel - Change Weapon Chat - T Enter Send To Chat H - Show Hide Chat C - Crouch Left Ctrl - Lie LMB - Fire RMB - Aim F - Pick Up Weapon R - Reload Left Shift - Run Space - Jump', 'English'),
('Missile Attack', 2998, 'Missile Attack Game Missile Attack troops, cities and villages are under air strikes. The enemy has launched dozens of missiles! Please command your troops to destroy the missiles and save thousands of innocent lives. The people of the country are counting on you! Pick up your weapons and destroy the missiles before they land. Missile Attack is an immersive game that tests your speed. Accept the challenge, act methodically and quickly, and strive for the highest score!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Stunt Witch 2', 2999, 'Stunt Witch 2 is a magical arcade adventure where you play as a brave little witch flying through the night sky on her trusty broom! Your mission? Dodge obstacles, perform daring mid-air stunts, and collect sparkling stars scattered across the sky. With easy controls and a charming cartoon style, Stunt Witch 2 offers fun, fast-paced flying action for players of all ages. Perfect your magic skills, explore enchanted skies, and become the ultimate stunt witch!', 'LEFT KEY ROTATE LEFT RIGHT KEY ROTATE RIGHT', 'English'),
('Zombie City Rescue', 3000, 'Zombie City Rescue is an intense action-strategy game where youre humanity&amp;rsquo;s last hope! The city has fallen to the undead, and it&amp;rsquo;s up to you to rescue survivors, eliminate zombies, and restore order in a world gone mad. How to play: Lead your rescue squad through zombie-infested streets. Save trapped civilians and escort them to safety. Use weapons, tools, and tactics to fight hordes of the undead. With thrilling missions, dangerous enemies, and heart-pounding action, Zombie City Rescue delivers nonstop excitement. Upgrade your squad, unlock powerful gear, and plan each rescue mission with care&amp;mdash;every move could mean life or death.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Paper Ball', 3001, 'Paper Ball is a fun and addictive line-drawing puzzle game! Use your finger to draw a path and guide the mischievous paper ball into the trash can. Along the way, you&amp;rsquo;ll encounter various obstacles &amp;mdash; how you cleverly avoid them and plan your route is all up to your creativity and smarts! Unleash your imagination, draw the perfect track, take on tougher challenges, and enjoy the relaxing yet brain-teasing fun!', 'Drag the left mouse button to draw a line', 'English'),
('Panda Kitchen Idle Tycoon', 3002, 'Want to become the best restaurant tycoon? You&amp;rsquo;ll build your own panda-themed food empire in Panda Kitchen: Idle Tycoon. Earn idle profits, and manage your way to success. Unlock new dining tables and kitchen equipment to improve efficiency. Recruiting chefs and servers to create an ultra-efficient restaurant team.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English'),
('Astro Adventure Tour Max', 3003, 'Astro Adventure Tour Max: Blast Off on a Planetary Quest! Calling all young space explorers! Buckle up for Astro Adventure Tour, an exciting game that will launch you on a cosmic journey through our solar system. Explore eight incredible planets, learning their unique features and collecting stardust knowledge along the way!', 'Learn it and match the planets Allow some time to load', 'English'),
('Truck Simulator Extreme Park', 3004, 'Get ready to test your precision and strategy in Truck Simulator Extreme Park! In this unique truck parking challenge, you dont drive the truck &amp;mdash; you draw the path! Sketch the perfect route from your truck to the finish line and watch as it follows your lead. But be careful &amp;mdash; sharp turns, tight spaces, and tricky obstacles stand in your way! Features: Draw-to-drive gameplay &amp;ndash; intuitive and fun Challenging levels that test your logic and planning Realistic environments and detailed truck models Increasing difficulty with new twists every level', 'mouse only', 'English'),
('Tincha Junior', 3005, 'Welcome to Tincha Junior, the ultimate gashapon prize-hunting adventure! Insert coins, spin machines, and collect all unique prizes, but choose wisely! Each day brings a fresh challenge with fixed prize distributions. Watch out: the CPU strategically blocks machines each turn, testing your planning skills. All machines hold every prize, but the final two are special rare treasures. Can you gather the full set using the fewest coins possible? Plan your spins carefully and master the art of efficient collecting in Tincha Junior!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'English');
INSERT INTO h5_blog_detail (title, h5_game_id, description, instructions, language) VALUES
('Sure Shot', 3006, 'Sure Shot is the online multiplayer in which you are a soldier dropped into the madness of warfare. Lace up your boots and get ready soldier as you will be pitted against another special ops team where you will play different game modes to find the ultimate squadron across the globe. You can choose to play with your friends in team deathmatch or play on your own in a free for all type mode. Web Dev &lt;a href=''https://www.toyourlead.com/''&gt;https://www.toyourlead.com/&lt;/a&gt; Objective of both is to defeat as many enemies as possible to finish with the highest score. There are plenty of big maps to play on. Good luck!', 'Movements A W D S Jump Space Long Jump Space Button Twice Run Left Shift Fire Left Mouse Button Change weapon Mouse Wheel 1 2 3 4 Pause Menu P Score Tab Pick Up E Interaction F Spawn Med Kit H Spawn Amo Kit J Change Amo Mode B', 'English');
